to school all by myself.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:05:55.270 --> 00:05:58.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah, I'll take over providing
the good morning kiss, then.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:05:58.110 --> 00:05:59.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You will not.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000162
00:05:59.650 --> 00:06:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But in our talk last night
you agreed with me that</b></Default>

c0000163
00:06:02.030 --> 00:06:03.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it was okay for us
to start living together.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:06:03.780 --> 00:06:05.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No I did not.</b></Default>

c0000165
00:06:05.910 --> 00:06:07.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You could always
just two-time them.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:06:07.780 --> 00:06:10.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then you could level yourself up
from a rascal into a scum bag.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:06:10.750 --> 00:06:13.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Knock it off with
the outlandish nonsense.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:06:13.790 --> 00:06:15.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, is that book interesting?</b></Default>

c0000169
00:06:15.960 --> 00:06:17.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, incredibly.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:06:17.630 --> 00:06:19.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It says,
"super string theory."</b></Default>

c0000171
00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:21.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that some theory that
involves Mai taking care</b></Default>

c0000172
00:06:22.010 --> 00:06:23.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of me in the future?</b></Default>

c0000173
00:06:23.380 --> 00:06:25.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, that would just
be deadbeat theory.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:06:25.430 --> 00:06:27.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Now you're just messing
with me, right?</b></Default>

c0000175
00:06:27.430 --> 00:06:29.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all laughing]</b></Default>

c0000176
00:06:29.140 --> 00:06:31.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, dead in
the eyes again today?</b></Default>

c0000177
00:06:31.270 --> 00:06:32.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know it.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:34.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wha--you're going
home already?</b></Default>

c0000179
00:06:34.520 --> 00:06:36.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm leaving early to take
my sister to the hospital</b></Default>

c0000180
00:06:36.810 --> 00:06:38.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for her check-up.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:06:41.070 --> 00:06:42.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then I'll see you
when I'm all finished.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:06:42.650 --> 00:06:43.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:06:44.070 --> 00:06:45.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll just be hanging out in
the waiting room.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:06:52.330 --> 00:06:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[stammers]</b></Default>

c0000185
00:06:54.620 --> 00:06:55.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000186
00:06:56.830 --> 00:06:58.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wait, Makinohara?</b></Default>

c0000187
00:06:58.540 --> 00:07:00.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah, this is, um...</b></Default>

c0000188
00:07:05.800 --> 00:07:07.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think it's around
the time he bumps into</b></Default>

c0000189
00:07:07.680 --> 00:07:09.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my younger version.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:07:10.470 --> 00:07:13.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The truth is I've always
had poor health</b></Default>

c0000191
00:07:13.930 --> 00:07:16.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I've been hospitalized
many times starting from when I</b></Default>

c0000192
00:07:16.140 --> 00:07:17.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was in elementary school.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:07:17.810 --> 00:07:19.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:07:19.270 --> 00:07:21.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's why it was hard for me
to bring up</b></Default>

c0000195
00:07:21.190 --> 00:07:22.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Hayate situation
to my parents.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:07:22.980 --> 00:07:24.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000197
00:07:24.110 --> 00:07:25.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Because
of my physical condition,</b></Default>

c0000198
00:07:25.950 --> 00:07:28.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they always just say yes
to anything I ask them</b></Default>

c0000199
00:07:28.200 --> 00:07:29.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no matter what.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:07:30.280 --> 00:07:33.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Part of me is really happy they
do that but at the same time</b></Default>

c0000201
00:07:33.500 --> 00:07:34.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's hard on me.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:07:35.250 --> 00:07:38.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It makes me feel so guilty
like I should apologize.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:07:40.130 --> 00:07:41.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Your parents have probably
already noticed</b></Default>

c0000204
00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:43.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you feel that way.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:07:43.250 --> 00:07:45.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I had to take a guess.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000206
00:07:45.630 --> 00:07:47.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I have a question for you.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:50.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How do you feel about your
mother and father exactly?</b></Default>

c0000208
00:07:50.100 --> 00:07:52.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I love them!
I really do!</b></Default>

c0000209
00:07:52.140 --> 00:07:53.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And have you ever
told them that?</b></Default>

c0000210
00:07:54.390 --> 00:07:56.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mm, I haven't.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:58.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- For me it's like this.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:07:58.350 --> 00:08:01.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"I love you" is way nicer
to hear than "I'm sorry."</b></Default>

c0000213
00:08:01.480 --> 00:08:04.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And an "I really love you"
would put me over the moon.</b></Default>

c0000214
00:08:05.030 --> 00:08:06.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone once told me this.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000215
00:08:06.740 --> 00:08:08.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hearing, "thank you,"
"you did your best,"</b></Default>

c0000216
00:08:08.450 --> 00:08:09.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and "I love you--"</b></Default>

c0000217
00:08:09.740 --> 00:08:11.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>those three things
just can't be beat.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:08:12.030 --> 00:08:14.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why I don't think
you should be afraid</b></Default>

c0000219
00:08:14.830 --> 00:08:16.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of letting your parents
spoil you.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:08:16.870 --> 00:08:18.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000221
00:08:19.500 --> 00:08:20.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000222
00:08:20.750 --> 00:08:22.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I...</b></Default>

c0000223
00:08:22.130 --> 00:08:23.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cat chirps]</b></Default>

c0000224
00:08:24.250 --> 00:08:26.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She said once she gets out
of the hospital</b></Default>

c0000225
00:08:26.210 --> 00:08:28.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she'll come and pick up Hayate.
- That's great news.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:08:30.340 --> 00:08:31.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- During the time when I
was speaking with</b></Default>

c0000227
00:08:31.930 --> 00:08:34.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the middle school Makinohara in
the hospital,</b></Default>

c0000228
00:08:34.390 --> 00:08:36.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were you existing in
my apartment by yourself</b></Default>

c0000229
00:08:36.640 --> 00:08:38.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the entire time, Shoko-san?</b></Default>

c0000230
00:08:38.310 --> 00:08:39.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh. Who could say?</b></Default>

c0000231
00:08:39.980 --> 00:08:42.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At the very least,
no one else has observed me.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:08:42.770 --> 00:08:44.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So it remains uncertain.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:08:45.150 --> 00:08:48.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess you could call
me Schrodinger's Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:08:48.110 --> 00:08:50.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I also wanted to ask about
your puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:08:50.910 --> 00:08:53.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wondered if it had anything
to do with your illness at all.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:08:53.410 --> 00:08:55.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, yes. Probably.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:08:57.700 --> 00:09:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Truth is,
I actually have heart disease.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:09:00.330 --> 00:09:01.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasping]</b></Default>

c0000239
00:09:01.540 --> 00:09:03.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Back when I
was in elementary school,</b></Default>

c0000240
00:09:03.250 --> 00:09:05.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Doctors said my condition
would make it difficult</b></Default>

c0000241
00:09:05.500 --> 00:09:07.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for me to live long enough
to graduate middle school.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:09:07.670 --> 00:09:08.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000243
00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:10.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So ever since then,</b></Default>

c0000244
00:09:10.510 --> 00:09:13.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my biggest dream was being able
to grow up and become an adult.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:09:14.010 --> 00:09:15.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to make it
to high school.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:09:15.970 --> 00:09:18.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to study at a college.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:19.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to be a grown-up.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:09:20.890 --> 00:09:22.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that's why I'm older.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:09:22.770 --> 00:09:24.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's how my younger self
imagines her future.</b></Default>

c0000250
00:09:24.940 --> 00:09:26.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The one she's always
been dreaming about.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:09:27.070 --> 00:09:28.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least that's what I think
it is.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:09:29.490 --> 00:09:31.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000253
00:09:31.530 --> 00:09:34.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, big sis, how long are you
planning on staying over there?</b></Default>

c0000254
00:09:34.870 --> 00:09:36.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Just a little more.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:09:36.950 --> 00:09:38.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'll be in touch
with you soon, okay?</b></Default>

c0000256
00:09:40.460 --> 00:09:42.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After listening to her story,</b></Default>

c0000257
00:09:42.170 --> 00:09:43.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no idea what
we should be doing.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:09:43.920 --> 00:09:45.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, tomorrow at least,</b></Default>

c0000259
00:09:45.880 --> 00:09:47.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll swing by
the hospital again.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:09:47.380 --> 00:09:49.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'd appreciate that, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:09:49.300 --> 00:09:50.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll see if Futaba will come.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:09:51.050 --> 00:09:52.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can leave it to us.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:54.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [breathing deeply]</b></Default>

c0000264
00:09:55.370 --> 00:09:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 10TH</b></Default>

c0000265
00:09:58.600 --> 00:10:00.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Let me confirm one thing.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:02.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From what you've explained,</b></Default>

c0000267
00:10:02.230 --> 00:10:04.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>middle school Shoko doesn't know
that she sometimes grows up.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:10:04.730 --> 00:10:06.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Am I understanding
that correctly?</b></Default>

c0000269
00:10:06.310 --> 00:10:08.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shoko-san told me
that she's never</b></Default>

c0000270
00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:12.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>met Makinohara directly before,
so she' probably doesn't know.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:10:15.700 --> 00:10:17.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[knocking]
- Yes?</b></Default>

c0000272
00:10:18.620 --> 00:10:20.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How are you feeling today?</b></Default>

c0000273
00:10:20.200 --> 00:10:22.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, you're here!
You really came by to visit me.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:10:23.040 --> 00:10:24.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And I brought Futaba along
with me, too.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:10:25.040 --> 00:10:26.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's good to see you.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:10:26.290 --> 00:10:27.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, you, too!</b></Default>

c0000277
00:10:28.040 --> 00:10:30.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I know this visit was sudden.
Is this okay?</b></Default>

c0000278
00:10:30.590 --> 00:10:32.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes. In fact, more than okay.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:10:32.920 --> 00:10:35.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm happy you're here!
- I'm glad.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:10:35.890 --> 00:10:37.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In the middle of studying?</b></Default>

c0000281
00:10:37.220 --> 00:10:40.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No. It's perfect timing,
though.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:10:40.270 --> 00:10:42.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I ask you two for
a little bit of advice?</b></Default>

c0000283
00:10:42.520 --> 00:10:43.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>both: Mm?</b></Default>

c0000284
00:10:44.810 --> 00:10:47.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- "Schedule for the future."</b></Default>

c0000285
00:10:47.150 --> 00:10:49.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is there something wrong
with it?</b></Default>

c0000286
00:10:49.190 --> 00:10:51.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's something everyone in
my class filled out when I</b></Default>

c0000287
00:10:51.570 --> 00:10:52.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was in fourth grade.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:10:52.940 --> 00:10:54.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't mention this last
time we talked</b></Default>

c0000289
00:10:54.820 --> 00:10:56.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but with my illness,</b></Default>

c0000290
00:10:56.450 --> 00:10:59.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I'm not able to get
the heart transplant I need,</b></Default>

c0000291
00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:00.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it seems pretty unlikely
I'll be able</b></Default>

c0000292
00:11:00.870 --> 00:11:02.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to even live through
middle school.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:04.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- A heart transplant.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:11:04.790 --> 00:11:07.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's why when the schedule
came up for the future,</b></Default>

c0000295
00:11:07.960 --> 00:11:10.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had so many things I wanted
to write down.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:11:10.550 --> 00:11:12.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I just couldn't bring myself
to write anything</b></Default>

c0000297
00:11:12.800 --> 00:11:14.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after graduating middle school.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:11:15.090 --> 00:11:17.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told myself that I'd love
to fill it out someday.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:11:17.720 --> 00:11:19.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But each time I tried,
I couldn't.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:11:19.510 --> 00:11:21.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the end I graduated
from elementary school</b></Default>

c0000301
00:11:22.060 --> 00:11:24.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without ever having completed
this assignment.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:11:24.310 --> 00:11:27.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-
But this is your handwriting,
isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000303
00:11:27.310 --> 00:11:31.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, but I definitely
didn't write those down.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:11:31.270 --> 00:11:33.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And there's no way you maybe
just forgot you did it?</b></Default>

c0000305
00:11:33.740 --> 00:11:35.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mm-mmm.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:11:35.150 --> 00:11:37.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I looked at it prior
to my hospitalization.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:11:37.360 --> 00:11:39.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm certain that part
was not written there.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:11:39.530 --> 00:11:41.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That really is strange.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:11:41.410 --> 00:11:43.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So were all these things
you wanted</b></Default>

c0000310
00:11:43.120 --> 00:11:44.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to write down back then,
Shoko-chan?</b></Default>

c0000311
00:11:44.790 --> 00:11:46.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's slightly different.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:11:46.290 --> 00:11:47.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd say if anything,</b></Default>

c0000313
00:11:47.960 --> 00:11:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's closer to what
I'd write down now.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:11:50.080 --> 00:11:53.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then what would you fill in
as continuations of that?</b></Default>

c0000315
00:11:53.300 --> 00:11:55.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-
Well first of all,
I'd like to go to college.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:11:55.630 --> 00:11:57.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It would be really nice
if I could find</b></Default>

c0000317
00:11:57.260 --> 00:11:58.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a wonderful boyfriend as well.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:11:58.970 --> 00:12:00.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then we'd start
living together</b></Default>

c0000319
00:12:00.930 --> 00:12:02.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and if that led
to us getting married,</b></Default>

c0000320
00:12:02.760 --> 00:12:03.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it'd be the best!</b></Default>

c0000321
00:12:04.060 --> 00:12:06.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- While you're still in college?
- Yes.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:12:06.100 --> 00:12:07.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My parents got married
to each other while they</b></Default>

c0000323
00:12:07.980 --> 00:12:09.270 line:90% align:center
