c0000324
00:12:09.350 --> 00:12:11.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is it okay if I take
a quick picture of this?</b></Default>

c0000325
00:12:11.400 --> 00:12:12.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sure.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:12:12.860 --> 00:12:14.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm going to spend some
more time thinking on it.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:12:14.230 --> 00:12:15.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[camera shutter clicks]</b></Default>

c0000328
00:12:16.190 --> 00:12:17.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For the time being,</b></Default>

c0000329
00:12:17.450 --> 00:12:18.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if we're going to define
