c0000336
00:12:34.000 --> 00:12:35.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ORGAN DONOR CARD</b></Default>

c0000337
00:12:35.420 --> 00:12:37.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then this is about all I
