c0000354
00:13:18.510 --> 00:13:20.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[knocking]
- Can I come in?</b></Default>

c0000355
00:13:20.300 --> 00:13:22.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, go ahead.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:13:22.640 --> 00:13:24.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You busy?
