c0000358
00:13:26.760 --> 00:13:28.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
You put a little tree up.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:13:28.640 --> 00:13:29.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:13:29.730 --> 00:13:31.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'm still hoping I can</b></Default>

c0000361
00:13:31.190 --> 00:13:33.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>be discharged before Christmas.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:13:33.150 --> 00:13:35.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And there's the illumination
at Enoshima.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:13:35.900 --> 00:13:38.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope I can go see it again
this year.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:13:38.150 --> 00:13:40.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The illumination at Enoshima,
