c0000376
00:14:06.260 --> 00:14:07.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we can go celebrate with that.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:14:07.760 --> 00:14:09.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, I'm looking forward
