c0000378
00:14:09.640 --> 00:14:12.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, by the way, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:14:12.690 --> 00:14:14.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About that thing from yesterday.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:14:15.900 --> 00:14:17.020 line:90% align:center
