c0000402
00:15:02.650 --> 00:15:05.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was really saved by you,
Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:15:07.950 --> 00:15:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The one that was saved
