00:15:30.850 --> 00:15:33.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps on sand]</b></Default>

c0000410
00:15:33.680 --> 00:15:34.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000411
00:15:35.520 --> 00:15:37.270 line:90% align:center
