c0000415
00:15:48.700 --> 00:15:50.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, I, uh--</b></Default>

c0000416
00:15:50.660 --> 00:15:52.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You can make excuses
