was attentively nursing you</b></Default>

c0000418
00:15:55.250 --> 00:15:56.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all afternoon anyway.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:15:56.830 --> 00:15:58.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you feeling any better yet?</b></Default>

c0000420
00:15:58.750 --> 00:16:00.290 line:90% align:center
