c0000434
00:16:26.900 --> 00:16:28.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think so.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:16:28.500 --> 00:16:30.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 13TH</b></Default>

c0000436
00:16:30.950 --> 00:16:33.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Futaba, you here?</b></Default>

c0000437
00:16:33.160 --> 00:16:35.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes. Yes.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:16:35.240 --> 00:16:37.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He just walked in.
