c0000446
00:16:53.470 --> 00:16:54.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why, yes, I am.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:16:54.850 --> 00:16:56.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Just to let you know,</b></Default>

c0000448
00:16:56.310 --> 00:16:58.640 line:90% align:center
