c0000459
00:17:21.960 --> 00:17:23.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>perceives her existence to be.</b></Default>

c0000460
00:17:23.790 --> 00:17:26.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is it not possible for her
