c0000461
00:17:26.630 --> 00:17:28.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that the younger Makinohara
is dreaming of?</b></Default>

c0000462
00:17:28.760 --> 00:17:30.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shoko-san seems to be
somewhere around college age</b></Default>

c0000463
00:17:31.050 --> 00:17:32.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the moment, right?</b></Default>

c0000464
00:17:32.390 --> 00:17:33.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you think happened
to the memories</b></Default>

c0000465
00:17:33.890 --> 00:17:35.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the six to seven years
between them?</b></Default>

c0000466
00:17:36.100 --> 00:17:37.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Maybe there's nothing.</b></Default>

c0000467
00:17:37.810 --> 00:17:40.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If the theory I formulated
