00:18:25.020 --> 00:18:26.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [giggles]</b></Default>

c0000482
00:18:26.190 --> 00:18:27.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's right here.</b></Default>

c0000483
00:18:29.780 --> 00:18:31.820 line:90% align:center
