c0000484
00:18:31.900 --> 00:18:33.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Before we get started today,</b></Default>

c0000485
00:18:33.360 --> 00:18:35.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to thank you both
for participating</b></Default>

c0000486
00:18:35.110 --> 00:18:36.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in our guided tour.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:18:36.320 --> 00:18:37.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, this way.</b></Default>

c0000488
00:18:42.250 --> 00:18:43.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doors squeak open]</b></Default>

c0000489
00:18:43.870 --> 00:18:45.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000490
00:18:49.250 --> 00:18:51.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Please, head inside.</b></Default>

c0000491
00:18:52.630 --> 00:18:54.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We offer the opportunity
to wear a wedding dress,</b></Default>

c0000492
00:18:54.680 --> 00:18:56.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you'd like.</b></Default>

c0000493
00:18:56.140 --> 00:18:57.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't think
I should right now.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:18:57.930 --> 00:18:59.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why not?
You should go for it.</b></Default>

c0000495
00:18:59.760 --> 00:19:01.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mm, but it's--</b></Default>

c0000496
00:19:01.100 --> 00:19:02.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Could I please make
the request?</b></Default>

c0000497
00:19:02.850 --> 00:19:04.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes. Of course.
Come this way.</b></Default>

c0000498
00:19:05.060 --> 00:19:06.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [laughs]</b></Default>

c0000499
00:19:13.030 --> 00:19:15.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to keep you waiting.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000500
00:19:21.740 --> 00:19:23.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- your mouth is gaping open.</b></Default>

c0000501
00:19:23.700 --> 00:19:25.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's just you look
so beautiful,</b></Default>

c0000502
00:19:25.460 --> 00:19:27.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was awestruck.
- If that's the case,</b></Default>

c0000503
00:19:27.630 --> 00:19:29.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the effort I put into picking
the perfect dress for you</b></Default>

c0000504
00:19:29.750 --> 00:19:30.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was more than worth it.</b></Default>

c0000505
00:19:30.920 --> 00:19:32.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Now then,
please take your time.</b></Default>

c0000506
00:19:32.760 --> 00:19:33.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door latches shut]</b></Default>

c0000507
00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:35.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000508
00:19:36.550 --> 00:19:39.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think a free guided tour
is enough to fulfill this wish?</b></Default>

c0000509
00:19:39.220 --> 00:19:40.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's something
you have to bring up</b></Default>

c0000510
00:19:40.720 --> 00:19:41.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with my younger self.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:19:42.010 --> 00:19:43.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You say that but you already</b></Default>

c0000512
00:19:43.350 --> 00:19:44.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>know the answer, don't you?</b></Default>

c0000513
00:19:44.890 --> 00:19:47.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Am I correct?
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000514
00:19:47.520 --> 00:19:49.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That scar you have
on your chest.</b></Default>

c0000515
00:19:52.110 --> 00:19:54.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That must mean you were able
to get the heart transplant.</b></Default>

c0000516
00:19:54.740 --> 00:19:55.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes.</b></Default>

c0000517
00:19:57.450 --> 00:20:00.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So then, Shoko-san,
you came from the future, right?</b></Default>

c0000518
00:20:00.320 --> 00:20:01.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [chuckles[</b></Default>

c0000519
00:20:02.280 --> 00:20:03.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you mad?</b></Default>

c0000520
00:20:03.620 --> 00:20:04.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's fine.</b></Default>

c0000521
00:20:06.080 --> 00:20:08.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm honestly just relieved
about all of it.</b></Default>

c0000522
00:20:08.620 --> 00:20:11.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makinohara is able
to receive the surgery</b></Default>

c0000523
00:20:11.090 --> 00:20:12.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she needs to recover.</b></Default>

c0000524
00:20:12.420 --> 00:20:14.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh-huh.
And it'll happen soon, too.</b></Default>

c0000525
00:20:14.920 --> 00:20:16.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My little self will receive
her transplant.</b></Default>

c0000526
00:20:17.010 --> 00:20:19.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And with that she will be cured
of her heart disease.</b></Default>

c0000527
00:20:19.430 --> 00:20:21.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And same thing
with this puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

c0000528
00:20:22.010 --> 00:20:24.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everything should be resolved by
the time Christmas comes</b></Default>

c0000529
00:20:24.390 --> 00:20:25.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to an end.
- Then...</b></Default>

c0000530
00:20:26.390 --> 00:20:27.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- When Christmas comes
to an end,</b></Default>

c0000531
00:20:28.060 --> 00:20:30.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so will the time I have
to spend together with you.</b></Default>

c0000532
00:20:31.110 --> 00:20:33.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So will you please give me
one last memory?</b></Default>

c0000533
00:20:34.070 --> 00:20:35.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And what did you have in mind?</b></Default>

c0000534
00:20:37.320 --> 00:20:39.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- A memory of my first love.</b></Default>

c0000535
00:20:43.830 --> 00:20:46.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I have no idea why you're
so fond of me, Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0000536
00:20:47.500 --> 00:20:49.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, there were a ton
of reasons for me</b></Default>

c0000537
00:20:49.290 --> 00:20:50.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to be attracted to you, but...</b></Default>

c0000538
00:20:50.750 --> 00:20:51.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, for starters,</b></Default>

c0000539
00:20:51.920 --> 00:20:52.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you were the one who gave me</b></Default>

c0000540
00:20:53.000 --> 00:20:54.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the opportunity to raise Hayate.</b></Default>

c0000541
00:20:54.630 --> 00:20:56.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's nothing.</b></Default>

c0000542
00:20:56.800 --> 00:21:00.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Also, when I was feeling
guilty about my parents,</b></Default>

c0000543
00:21:00.300 --> 00:21:02.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you were the one that taught me
it was better</b></Default>

c0000544
00:21:02.090 --> 00:21:03.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to tell them thank you
and I love you.</b></Default>

c0000545
00:21:03.760 --> 00:21:06.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'm sorry.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000546
00:21:07.020 --> 00:21:10.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- When I was in my hospital bed
overcome with anxiety,</b></Default>

c0000547
00:21:10.350 --> 00:21:12.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you were the one who came
to visit me every day.</b></Default>

c0000548
00:21:12.810 --> 00:21:15.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's why my first love
has remained</b></Default>

c0000549
00:21:15.480 --> 00:21:17.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in my heart ever since</b></Default>

c0000550
00:21:17.230 --> 00:21:19.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I've been unable
to share that with anyone else.</b></Default>

c0000551
00:21:19.900 --> 00:21:23.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And so I need you to take proper
responsibility for it, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000552
00:21:23.740 --> 00:21:25.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What exactly should I
do,
then?</b></Default>

c0000553
00:21:26.990 --> 00:21:29.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'd like you
to spend Christmas Eve with me.</b></Default>

c0000554
00:21:30.040 --> 00:21:32.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's watch the illumination
at Enoshima together.</b></Default>

c0000555
00:21:33.040 --> 00:21:35.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But that's--
- As far as your plans go,</b></Default>

c0000556
00:21:35.710 --> 00:21:37.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede will be staying over
at your grandfather's starting</b></Default>

c0000557
00:21:37.960 --> 00:21:39.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the 23rd.
- I dunno.</b></Default>

c0000558
00:21:39.630 --> 00:21:41.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's the first I've heard
of that.</b></Default>

c0000559
00:21:41.180 --> 00:21:43.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And besides--
- Then there's Mai.</b></Default>

c0000560
00:21:43.720 --> 00:21:45.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'll be free
from early evening.</b></Default>

c0000561
00:21:45.470 --> 00:21:47.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- Please decide.</b></Default>

c0000562
00:21:48.020 --> 00:21:50.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How you'll spend it.
Either with me or with Mai.</b></Default>

c0000563
00:21:50.940 --> 00:21:53.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shoko-san, I don't--
- You don't have</b></Default>

c0000564
00:21:53.230 --> 00:21:54.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to say anything.
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000565
00:21:55.020 --> 00:21:56.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I will be waiting, though,
'kay?</b></Default>

c0000566
00:21:57.190 --> 00:21:59.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At 6:00 p.m. on the 24th.</b></Default>

c0000567
00:21:59.690 --> 00:22:01.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be at the entrance
to Bentembashi,</b></Default>

c0000568
00:22:01.780 --> 00:22:03.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>right by the dragon lantern.</b></Default>

c0000569
00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:06.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How did your date
end up going?</b></Default>

c0000570
00:22:06.780 --> 00:22:08.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Just like your
theory suggested.</b></Default>

c0000571
00:22:08.540 --> 00:22:10.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She had a scar from an operation
on her chest.</b></Default>

c0000572
00:22:10.750 --> 00:22:13.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So you saw Shoko-san's
breasts, then.</b></Default>

c0000573
00:22:13.500 --> 00:22:16.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- For the record I did not make
her get naked to see it.</b></Default>

c0000574
00:22:16.250 --> 00:22:19.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But anyway, how did she manage
to come here from the future?</b></Default>

c0000575
00:22:19.760 --> 00:22:21.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't think saying she
came here from the future</b></Default>

c0000576
00:22:21.720 --> 00:22:22.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is quite accurate.</b></Default>

c0000577
00:22:22.720 --> 00:22:23.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It would be better to say</b></Default>

c0000578
00:22:23.800 --> 00:22:25.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she arrived at the future.</b></Default>

c0000579
00:22:25.510 --> 00:22:27.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What do you mean,
"Arrived at the future?"</b></Default>

c0000580
00:22:27.510 --> 00:22:29.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- When we visited Shoko-chan
together the other day,</b></Default>

c0000581
00:22:29.890 --> 00:22:32.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she was being whiny
for once unlike her usual self.</b></Default>

c0000582
00:22:32.850 --> 00:22:34.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was even wishing
for her body</b></Default>

c0000583
00:22:34.350 --> 00:22:36.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to just stop growing altogether.</b></Default>

c0000584
00:22:36.310 --> 00:22:38.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But when I talked to her
she told me that she wanted</b></Default>

c0000585
00:22:38.770 --> 00:22:40.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to show her parents how she'd
end up as an adult.</b></Default>

c0000586
00:22:40.990 --> 00:22:44.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's possible the Shoko-chan
that wishes to become an adult</b></Default>

c0000587
00:22:44.240 --> 00:22:47.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the one who refuses
to grow up completely</b></Default>

c0000588
00:22:47.490 --> 00:22:49.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>resulted in two existences
at odds with each other</b></Default>

c0000589
00:22:49.950 --> 00:22:51.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and that caused
her puberty syndrome then.</b></Default>

c0000590
00:22:52.040 --> 00:22:53.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What do you mean by that?</b></Default>

c0000591
00:22:54.250 --> 00:22:56.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- First there's the Shoko-chan
that refuses to grow up.</b></Default>

c0000592
00:22:57.000 --> 00:22:58.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's probably trying
desperately</b></Default>

c0000593
00:22:58.960 --> 00:23:01.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to stop her internal clock
from ticking forward.</b></Default>

c0000594
00:23:02.380 --> 00:23:04.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What if as a result the world
from her perspective</b></Default>

c0000595
00:23:04.970 --> 00:23:07.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has drastically slowed down
and everything in that world</b></Default>

c0000596
00:23:08.050 --> 00:23:09.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is moving in slow motion to her?</b></Default>

c0000597
00:23:12.560 --> 00:23:15.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What if we and the Shoko-chan
that wishes to become an adult</b></Default>

c0000598
00:23:15.640 --> 00:23:18.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>observe that world
from the one we're experiencing?</b></Default>

c0000599
00:23:18.610 --> 00:23:20.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How would it appear relative
to us?</b></Default>

c0000600
00:23:24.320 --> 00:23:26.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So we're talking
quantum physics again.</b></Default>

c0000601
00:23:26.410 --> 00:23:28.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My favorite subject.
- Not quite.</b></Default>

c0000602
00:23:28.620 --> 00:23:31.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This time it's about the theory
of relativity.</b></Default>

c0000603
00:23:31.200 --> 00:23:33.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's like the story
of the fisherman</b></Default>

c0000604
00:23:33.200 --> 00:23:35.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that returns from Ryugu Palace
and several decades</b></Default>

c0000605
00:23:35.750 --> 00:23:37.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>had passed on land.</b></Default>

c0000606
00:23:37.250 --> 00:23:39.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So Shoko-san is kinda
like Urashima Taro.</b></Default>

c0000607
00:23:40.040 --> 00:23:41.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's right.</b></Default>

c0000608
00:23:41.420 --> 00:23:43.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Time has moved along
at a much faster pace</b></Default>

c0000609
00:23:43.670 --> 00:23:45.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for Shoko-chan who refused
to grow up.</b></Default>

c0000610
00:23:45.760 --> 00:23:48.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And as a result she arrived at
the future long before we did.</b></Default>

c0000611
00:23:50.970 --> 00:23:52.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]
- I'm home.</b></Default>

c0000612
00:23:52.930 --> 00:23:55.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah, big brother.
Welcome home.</b></Default>

c0000613
00:23:56.060 --> 00:23:58.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yep, he literally just
walked through the door.</b></Default>

c0000614
00:23:58.980 --> 00:24:01.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure. I got it.
See you later.</b></Default>

c0000615
00:24:01.900 --> 00:24:03.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Who was that just now?</b></Default>

c0000616
00:24:03.230 --> 00:24:04.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, Dad just called.</b></Default>

c0000617
00:24:05.320 --> 00:24:06.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was saying that Grandpa
and Grandma</b></Default>

c0000618
00:24:06.860 --> 00:24:08.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>had been really wanting
to see me.</b></Default>

c0000619
00:24:08.110 --> 00:24:09.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasping]</b></Default>

c0000620
00:24:09.410 --> 00:24:11.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [chuckles]
By the way,</b></Default>

c0000621
00:24:11.160 --> 00:24:13.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai called here not all
that long ago, too.</b></Default>

c0000622
00:24:13.700 --> 00:24:15.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She wants you to pick her up
at the train station</b></Default>

c0000623
00:24:15.370 --> 00:24:16.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>around 9:00 o'clock.</b></Default>

c0000624
00:24:16.870 --> 00:24:18.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Apparently she has something
she wants to talk about.</b></Default>

c0000625
00:24:18.870 --> 00:24:20.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Something like--</b></Default>

c0000626
00:24:20.420 --> 00:24:22.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I do have to ask
that you keep today's chat</b></Default>

c0000627
00:24:22.340 --> 00:24:23.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a secret from others.</b></Default>

c0000628
00:24:23.670 --> 00:24:25.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it leads
to the future changing,</b></Default>

c0000629
00:24:25.420 --> 00:24:27.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I might not have my surgery
and that'd be awful.</b></Default>

c0000630
00:24:28.430 --> 00:24:30.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000631
00:24:30.090 --> 00:24:32.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The film shoot is going well
and moving at a good pace.</b></Default>

c0000632
00:24:32.760 --> 00:24:35.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So for now I don't have anything
planned from the afternoon on.</b></Default>

c0000633
00:24:35.470 --> 00:24:38.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- That's why on the 24th,</b></Default>

c0000634
00:24:38.480 --> 00:24:40.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we're going on a date.
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000635
00:24:42.020 --> 00:24:44.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How about the illumination
at Enoshima?</b></Default>

c0000636
00:24:44.690 --> 00:24:45.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000637
00:24:49.450 --> 00:24:51.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'd like to see the jellyfish
at the aquarium.</b></Default>

c0000638
00:24:52.070 --> 00:24:54.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Te exhibit being advertised on
the trains lately?</b></Default>

c0000639
00:24:54.700 --> 00:24:55.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, that.</b></Default>

c0000640
00:24:56.250 --> 00:24:58.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got kinda curious after
seeing them every day.</b></Default>

c0000641
00:24:58.540 --> 00:25:00.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I didn't know you
liked jellyfish.</b></Default>

c0000642
00:25:00.580 --> 00:25:01.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm pretty sure I'd like them</b></Default>

c0000643
00:25:01.790 --> 00:25:03.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I got to see them with you,
Mai.</b></Default>

c0000644
00:25:03.170 --> 00:25:04.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah.</b></Default>

c0000645
00:25:05.090 --> 00:25:06.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then one I've finished my work
for the day,</b></Default>

c0000646
00:25:06.840 --> 00:25:08.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll head straight over.</b></Default>

c0000647
00:25:08.470 --> 00:25:10.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How does meeting in front
of the aquarium at 6:00 sound?</b></Default>

c0000648
00:25:11.390 --> 00:25:12.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Great.</b></Default>

c0000649
00:25:12.410 --> 00:25:12.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 14TH
- Great.</b></Default>

c0000650
00:25:12.430 --> 00:25:14.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 14TH</b></Default>

c0000651
00:25:14.600 --> 00:25:15.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000652
00:25:15.930 --> 00:25:17.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, something good happen
to you?</b></Default>

c0000653
00:25:18.060 --> 00:25:19.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000654
00:25:19.270 --> 00:25:20.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- 'Cause I saw you grinning.</b></Default>

c0000655
00:25:20.940 --> 00:25:23.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But I think I'm the one who
should be asking you that, Koga.</b></Default>

c0000656
00:25:23.480 --> 00:25:24.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? How come?</b></Default>

c0000657
00:25:24.940 --> 00:25:26.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Your upper arms look
a little chubbier.</b></Default>

c0000658
00:25:27.030 --> 00:25:28.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
You're the worst, Sakuta!</b></Default>

c0000659
00:25:28.780 --> 00:25:31.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't believe ya!
- [chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000660
00:25:33.740 --> 00:25:35.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry.
Is it too late to visit?</b></Default>

c0000661
00:25:35.740 --> 00:25:37.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No.</b></Default>

c0000662
00:25:38.040 --> 00:25:40.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll make sure to get here
a bit earlier tomorrow, though.</b></Default>

c0000663
00:25:40.750 --> 00:25:41.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm?</b></Default>

c0000664
00:25:43.040 --> 00:25:44.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's another new entry.</b></Default>

c0000665
00:25:44.840 --> 00:25:46.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There is, yes.</b></Default>

c0000666
00:25:48.090 --> 00:25:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000667
00:25:50.170 --> 00:25:53.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My health hasn't been doing
the best.</b></Default>

c0000668
00:25:54.260 --> 00:25:56.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The symptoms are being
controlled with medication</b></Default>

c0000669
00:25:56.390 --> 00:25:59.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for now but it won't work
for me in the long term.</b></Default>

c0000670
00:25:59.980 --> 00:26:01.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.</b></Default>

c0000671
00:26:01.560 --> 00:26:03.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes. So that's why...</b></Default>

c0000672
00:26:05.520 --> 00:26:08.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like to ask that you
don't come to visit me anymore.</b></Default>

c0000673
00:26:09.990 --> 00:26:10.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No way.</b></Default>

c0000674
00:26:10.990 --> 00:26:12.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000675
00:26:12.530 --> 00:26:14.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll come tomorrow
and the day after that, too.</b></Default>

c0000676
00:26:14.700 --> 00:26:17.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, there might be some days
I can't come because of work.</b></Default>

c0000677
00:26:18.580 --> 00:26:20.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But for the most part
until you're discharged,</b></Default>

c0000678
00:26:20.700 --> 00:26:21.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll visit you every day.</b></Default>

c0000679
00:26:21.870 --> 00:26:23.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But I--I will...</b></Default>

c0000680
00:26:24.960 --> 00:26:25.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will...</b></Default>

c0000681
00:26:28.800 --> 00:26:29.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000682
00:26:32.670 --> 00:26:35.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makinohara, you really gave
it your best.</b></Default>

c0000683
00:26:35.090 --> 00:26:37.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A truly valiant effort.</b></Default>

c0000684
00:26:37.350 --> 00:26:39.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [sniffles]
Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000685
00:26:39.520 --> 00:26:43.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The truth is all that--</b></Default>

c0000686
00:26:43.480 --> 00:26:45.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all that I ever wished for all
this time was to not have</b></Default>

c0000687
00:26:45.730 --> 00:26:46.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>an illness at all!</b></Default>

c0000688
00:26:47.020 --> 00:26:49.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why did it have to be me?</b></Default>

c0000689
00:26:49.400 --> 00:26:54.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not fair when everyone
else gets to keep living!</b></Default>

c0000690
00:26:54.820 --> 00:26:56.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just...</b></Default>

c0000691
00:26:57.410 --> 00:27:00.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I know these days have been
so long and hard for you</b></Default>

c0000692
00:27:00.540 --> 00:27:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and that you've been doing
your best.</b></Default>

c0000693
00:27:02.410 --> 00:27:03.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's okay now.</b></Default>

c0000694
00:27:04.290 --> 00:27:05.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't have to do
it on your own.</b></Default>

c0000695
00:27:06.460 --> 00:27:07.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be here tomorrow, too.</b></Default>

c0000696
00:27:08.500 --> 00:27:09.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the next day.</b></Default>

c0000697
00:27:10.090 --> 00:27:11.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is a promise.</b></Default>

c0000698
00:27:11.920 --> 00:27:13.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You really mean that?</b></Default>

c0000699
00:27:13.880 --> 00:27:15.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasping]</b></Default>

c0000700
00:27:15.760 --> 00:27:17.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000701
00:27:17.340 --> 00:27:18.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000702
00:27:18.640 --> 00:27:19.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makinohara?</b></Default>

c0000703
00:27:20.390 --> 00:27:22.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makinohara!</b></Default>

c0000704
00:27:22.100 --> 00:27:23.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Makinohara's condition
is critical.</b></Default>

c0000705
00:27:23.980 --> 00:27:25.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Confirm with
the operating room, stat.</b></Default>

c0000706
00:27:25.850 --> 00:27:27.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- OR's here.
- It'll be okay, Shoko.</b></Default>

c0000707
00:27:27.150 --> 00:27:29.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Vitals?
- [gasping]</b></Default>

c0000708
00:27:29.230 --> 00:27:30.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all speaking at once]</b></Default>

c0000709
00:27:31.980 --> 00:27:33.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ow, damn!</b></Default>

c0000710
00:27:33.490 --> 00:27:35.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000711
00:27:35.110 --> 00:27:36.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000712
00:27:36.910 --> 00:27:38.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's going on?</b></Default>

c0000713
00:27:38.370 --> 00:27:39.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000714
00:27:39.830 --> 00:27:41.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why does this have
to happen right now?</b></Default>

c0000715
00:27:42.240 --> 00:27:43.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000716
00:27:44.000 --> 00:27:45.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could it be possible...</b></Default>

c0000717
00:27:45.960 --> 00:27:47.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That my...</b></Default>

c0000718
00:27:47.330 --> 00:27:49.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000719
00:27:55.920 --> 00:27:57.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Your heart is racing
right now, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000720
00:27:57.970 --> 00:28:00.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Could you not get
me worked up, please?</b></Default>

c0000721
00:28:00.390 --> 00:28:01.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's the same for me,
you know.</b></Default>

c0000722
00:28:02.060 --> 00:28:04.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I'm here with you,
my heart races.</b></Default>

c0000723
00:28:04.680 --> 00:28:05.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I mean it.</b></Default>

c0000724
00:28:06.060 --> 00:28:07.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's bad for my scar,
so please stop.</b></Default>

c0000725
00:28:07.770 --> 00:28:09.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It'll be all right.</b></Default>

c0000726
00:28:09.190 --> 00:28:11.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm certain it will heal.</b></Default>

c0000727
00:28:11.860 --> 00:28:14.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rest assured the wound
in your heart</b></Default>

c0000728
00:28:14.690 --> 00:28:17.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the wound on your chest,
I'm going to heal both of them.</b></Default>

c0000729
00:28:18.030 --> 00:28:18.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000730
00:28:20.200 --> 00:28:22.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I will make sure of it.
[giggles]</b></Default>

c0000731
00:28:28.370 --> 00:28:29.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

c0000732
00:28:30.540 --> 00:28:31.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hi, Sakuta.
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000733
00:28:32.590 --> 00:28:34.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0000734
00:28:34.500 --> 00:28:36.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I got a phone call saying
you suddenly collapsed.</b></Default>

c0000735
00:28:36.720 --> 00:28:37.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was quite a shock.</b></Default>

c0000736
00:28:38.050 --> 00:28:39.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000737
00:28:40.510 --> 00:28:42.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I was just dreaming.</b></Default>

c0000738
00:28:43.100 --> 00:28:45.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was about when I first
met you a few years ago.</b></Default>

c0000739
00:28:45.640 --> 00:28:47.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah.</b></Default>

c0000740
00:28:48.230 --> 00:28:50.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then I remembered
this happened before.</b></Default>

c0000741
00:28:51.310 --> 00:28:53.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where this scar showed up across
my chest and...</b></Default>

c0000742
00:28:55.070 --> 00:28:56.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0000743
00:28:57.610 --> 00:28:59.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The heart that's inside
of your chest,</b></Default>

c0000744
00:28:59.610 --> 00:29:01.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's actually my heart,
isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000745
00:29:01.620 --> 00:29:02.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000746
00:29:03.120 --> 00:29:04.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000747
00:29:05.330 --> 00:29:08.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew you'd probably figure
it out eventually.</b></Default>

c0000748
00:29:09.920 --> 00:29:13.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was--I was given
a future by you, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000749
00:29:15.420 --> 00:29:16.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000750
00:29:17.210 --> 00:29:19.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Just now,
what did you mean?</b></Default>

c0000751
00:29:20.300 --> 00:29:22.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rain pattering]</b></Default>

c0000752
00:29:23.800 --> 00:29:25.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In ten days,</b></Default>

c0000753
00:29:25.260 --> 00:29:27.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>meaning on the 24th of December,</b></Default>

c0000754
00:29:27.810 --> 00:29:31.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on that day in the afternoon
it begins to snow.</b></Default>

c0000755
00:29:31.770 --> 00:29:34.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>While Sakuta is on the way
to the location that he promised</b></Default>

c0000756
00:29:34.610 --> 00:29:36.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to meet up with you, Mai,</b></Default>

c0000757
00:29:36.190 --> 00:29:38.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he was involved in
a bad traffic accident due</b></Default>

c0000758
00:29:38.530 --> 00:29:39.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the inclement weather.</b></Default>

c0000759
00:29:39.990 --> 00:29:41.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But how could you know
that would happen?</b></Default>

c0000760
00:29:41.910 --> 00:29:44.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That would be because I
came here from the future.</b></Default>

c0000761
00:29:44.160 --> 00:29:45.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000762
00:29:45.530 --> 00:29:46.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000763
00:29:46.660 --> 00:29:47.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's the truth.</b></Default>

c0000764
00:29:48.040 --> 00:29:50.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta was transported
to the hospital.</b></Default>

c0000765
00:29:50.250 --> 00:29:52.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He never regained consciousness.</b></Default>

c0000766
00:29:52.370 --> 00:29:55.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Soon after that he
was declared to be brain dead.</b></Default>

c0000767
00:29:55.130 --> 00:29:57.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then when they went through
Sakuta's belongings,</b></Default>

c0000768
00:29:57.750 --> 00:29:59.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they found his donor card.</b></Default>

c0000769
00:29:59.420 --> 00:30:00.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because of that,</b></Default>

c0000770
00:30:00.630 --> 00:30:02.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was miraculously able
to receive</b></Default>

c0000771
00:30:02.430 --> 00:30:03.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a heart transplant in time.</b></Default>

c0000772
00:30:03.890 --> 00:30:05.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
I see.</b></Default>

c0000773
00:30:06.430 --> 00:30:09.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I found out about everything
after the operation.</b></Default>

c0000774
00:30:09.980 --> 00:30:13.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I went to tell Sakuta
my operation was successful...</b></Default>

c0000775
00:30:13.940 --> 00:30:17.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was Mai that ended up
telling me what had transpired.</b></Default>

c0000776
00:30:18.480 --> 00:30:21.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So please, drop your plans
and have a nice,</b></Default>

c0000777
00:30:21.400 --> 00:30:23.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>quiet at-home Christmas date
this year.</b></Default>

c0000778
00:30:23.410 --> 00:30:25.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But that means--
- It's going to be fine.</b></Default>

c0000779
00:30:25.910 --> 00:30:28.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know how it seems but my
young self has a bit of time.</b></Default>

c0000780
00:30:29.080 --> 00:30:31.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please have some faith
in modern medicine.</b></Default>

c0000781
00:30:31.120 --> 00:30:32.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000782
00:30:32.410 --> 00:30:34.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Now, it's dangerous
for me to stay</b></Default>

c0000783
00:30:34.500 --> 00:30:36.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in this hospital for too long.</b></Default>

c0000784
00:30:36.630 --> 00:30:38.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I'll go ahead and head back.</b></Default>

c0000785
00:30:39.090 --> 00:30:42.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And Mai, I trust you
to take care of him.</b></Default>

c0000786
00:30:46.970 --> 00:30:49.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[train pattering]</b></Default>

c0000787
00:30:51.140 --> 00:30:52.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I wish it was all a lie.</b></Default>

c0000788
00:30:55.900 --> 00:30:57.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So Mai, listen.</b></Default>

c0000789
00:30:57.610 --> 00:30:59.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You should know I have
no intention of breaking up.</b></Default>

c0000790
00:30:59.820 --> 00:31:00.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000791
00:31:01.030 --> 00:31:02.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We have to change plans</b></Default>

c0000792
00:31:02.360 --> 00:31:04.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for our Christmas Eve date,
though.</b></Default>

c0000793
00:31:04.200 --> 00:31:07.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nodoka will be away doing a show
so we can spend it at my place,</b></Default>

c0000794
00:31:08.030 --> 00:31:09.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just the two of us.</b></Default>

c0000795
00:31:09.580 --> 00:31:12.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And for New Years we'll do
our shrine visit together.</b></Default>

c0000796
00:31:12.580 --> 00:31:15.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'll be problematic with all
the people around on</b></Default>

c0000797
00:31:15.120 --> 00:31:18.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the day itself so maybe around
the end of winter break?</b></Default>

c0000798
00:31:18.290 --> 00:31:19.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That sounds good.</b></Default>

c0000799
00:31:19.800 --> 00:31:21.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In February I'll make you
some chocolate</b></Default>

c0000800
00:31:21.630 --> 00:31:23.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for Valentine's day.</b></Default>

c0000801
00:31:23.170 --> 00:31:25.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come spring I'm going
to be graduating high school</b></Default>

c0000802
00:31:25.880 --> 00:31:28.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I'll be a strict tutor
so brace yourself for that.</b></Default>

c0000803
00:31:29.470 --> 00:31:31.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then a year after
that we'll be going</b></Default>

c0000804
00:31:31.430 --> 00:31:32.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the same college together.</b></Default>

c0000805
00:31:38.190 --> 00:31:39.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why...</b></Default>

c0000806
00:31:40.480 --> 00:31:42.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want you to choose
a future with me, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000807
00:31:43.400 --> 00:31:45.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is my request to you.</b></Default>

c0000808
00:31:45.820 --> 00:31:46.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000809
00:31:47.070 --> 00:31:48.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I won't stay over tonight.</b></Default>

c0000810
00:31:48.570 --> 00:31:50.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Right.</b></Default>

c0000811
00:31:50.700 --> 00:31:52.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, goodnight.</b></Default>

c0000812
00:31:52.790 --> 00:31:53.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Goodnight.
Sleep well.</b></Default>

c0000813
00:31:57.000 --> 00:31:57.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000814
00:32:05.050 --> 00:32:07.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[melancholic music]</b></Default>

c0000815
00:32:08.010 --> 00:32:14.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000816
00:32:25.950 --> 00:32:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 18TH</b></Default>

c0000817
00:32:28.160 --> 00:32:30.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000818
00:32:36.200 --> 00:32:39.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[train wheels clacking]</b></Default>

c0000819
00:32:42.790 --> 00:32:43.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No club?</b></Default>

c0000820
00:32:44.000 --> 00:32:45.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How rare.</b></Default>

c0000821
00:32:45.880 --> 00:32:47.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I
saw you walking home
so I decided</b></Default>

c0000822
00:32:47.880 --> 00:32:49.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to skip activities today
and take a break.</b></Default>

c0000823
00:32:49.890 --> 00:32:51.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you confessing your love?</b></Default>

c0000824
00:32:52.510 --> 00:32:55.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa, have you
been avoiding me lately?</b></Default>

c0000825
00:32:55.350 --> 00:32:56.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000826
00:32:56.930 --> 00:32:58.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're imagining it.</b></Default>

c0000827
00:32:58.230 --> 00:32:59.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Just so you know,</b></Default>

c0000828
00:32:59.520 --> 00:33:01.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm aware that you collapsed
on Sunday.</b></Default>

c0000829
00:33:02.110 --> 00:33:05.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And also about how Shoko-chan
is now in the ICU.</b></Default>

c0000830
00:33:05.190 --> 00:33:06.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I went to
the hospital yesterday.</b></Default>

c0000831
00:33:06.820 --> 00:33:08.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.</b></Default>

c0000832
00:33:08.150 --> 00:33:10.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you already have an idea.</b></Default>

c0000833
00:33:10.200 --> 00:33:12.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I
thought about all
the possibilities.</b></Default>

c0000834
00:33:12.320 --> 00:33:14.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At this point it's become clear
that something happened</b></Default>

c0000835
00:33:14.620 --> 00:33:16.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to your scar every time
Shoko-san showed up.</b></Default>

c0000836
00:33:17.370 --> 00:33:19.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're amazing.</b></Default>

c0000837
00:33:19.540 --> 00:33:22.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm assuming that Shoko-chan
and Shoko-san are unable</b></Default>

c0000838
00:33:22.130 --> 00:33:24.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to see each other due
to their quantum properties.</b></Default>

c0000839
00:33:24.630 --> 00:33:27.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However you've interacted
directly with Shoko-san</b></Default>

c0000840
00:33:27.300 --> 00:33:30.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>several times despite sharing
a portion of the same existence.</b></Default>

c0000841
00:33:32.010 --> 00:33:34.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Currently there are two copies
of your heart present which</b></Default>

c0000842
00:33:34.390 --> 00:33:36.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>aren't supposed to be able
to exist simultaneously</b></Default>

c0000843
00:33:37.020 --> 00:33:38.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and that's why you have
that scar running across</b></Default>

c0000844
00:33:38.730 --> 00:33:39.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your chest, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000845
00:33:41.850 --> 00:33:43.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000846
00:33:43.440 --> 00:33:46.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said I was gonna get
run over by a car on the 24th.</b></Default>

c0000847
00:33:47.860 --> 00:33:50.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And Sakurajima knows about all
of this?</b></Default>

c0000848
00:33:50.530 --> 00:33:52.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes. She heard everything
together with me.</b></Default>

c0000849
00:33:52.990 --> 00:33:55.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's not really my place
to say too much more</b></Default>

c0000850
00:33:55.410 --> 00:33:57.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you two should really talk
it out.</b></Default>

c0000851
00:33:58.290 --> 00:33:59.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, you're right.</b></Default>

c0000852
00:34:01.620 --> 00:34:02.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000853
00:34:04.080 --> 00:34:05.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't--</b></Default>

c0000854
00:34:07.840 --> 00:34:09.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Want this.</b></Default>

c0000855
00:34:09.130 --> 00:34:12.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[train wheels clacking]</b></Default>

c0000856
00:34:14.930 --> 00:34:16.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How's your exam
studying going?</b></Default>

c0000857
00:34:17.310 --> 00:34:19.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You won't wear the bunny girl
outfit while you tutor me</b></Default>

c0000858
00:34:19.470 --> 00:34:21.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so unfortunately
my progress stalled.</b></Default>

c0000859
00:34:21.520 --> 00:34:23.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If I wore a bunny girl outfit
your progress would stall in</b></Default>

c0000860
00:34:24.060 --> 00:34:25.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a different way, wouldn't it?</b></Default>

c0000861
00:34:25.480 --> 00:34:26.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I might make progress
somewhere else, though.</b></Default>

c0000862
00:34:26.900 --> 00:34:27.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Dummy.</b></Default>

c0000863
00:34:29.110 --> 00:34:30.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So Mai, listen.</b></Default>

c0000864
00:34:30.440 --> 00:34:32.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, quick question
about Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000865
00:34:32.490 --> 00:34:34.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh--
- Didn't she mention she wanted</b></Default>

c0000866
00:34:34.820 --> 00:34:36.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to get a haircut before going
to see her grandparents?</b></Default>

c0000867
00:34:37.080 --> 00:34:38.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000868
00:34:38.410 --> 00:34:39.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There's a makeup artist I know</b></Default>

c0000869
00:34:39.740 --> 00:34:41.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that has a salon in Chigasaki.</b></Default>

c0000870
00:34:41.500 --> 00:34:43.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If Kaede's up for it,
we should take her there.</b></Default>

c0000871
00:34:43.460 --> 00:34:44.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, really?</b></Default>

c0000872
00:34:45.330 --> 00:34:47.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If she's open
to going Sunday afternoon,</b></Default>

c0000873
00:34:47.290 --> 00:34:49.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can tag along.
So could you ask her for me?</b></Default>

c0000874
00:34:50.050 --> 00:34:51.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sure. Got it.</b></Default>

c0000875
00:34:51.380 --> 00:34:53.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, I wanted to--
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000876
00:34:53.470 --> 00:34:55.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like my break is about
to end.</b></Default>

c0000877
00:34:55.220 --> 00:34:57.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll call you again tomorrow.
See you.</b></Default>

c0000878
00:34:58.180 --> 00:34:59.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone beeping]</b></Default>

c0000879
00:35:00.020 --> 00:35:00.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000880
00:35:02.250 --> 00:35:04.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 21ST</b></Default>

c0000881
00:35:05.060 --> 00:35:07.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think it might be nice
to lighten up this area</b></Default>

c0000882
00:35:07.360 --> 00:35:08.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a bit more.
- Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000883
00:35:08.820 --> 00:35:10.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What are you doing here,
Toyohama?</b></Default>

c0000884
00:35:10.860 --> 00:35:13.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I had an appointment here
today, too. Problem?</b></Default>

c0000885
00:35:14.030 --> 00:35:16.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, the Christmas Eve
situation.</b></Default>

c0000886
00:35:16.200 --> 00:35:18.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?
- I'm heading straight home</b></Default>

c0000887
00:35:18.120 --> 00:35:20.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after my show is over.
- Don't worry.</b></Default>

c0000888
00:35:20.660 --> 00:35:22.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll make sure that we
leave enough cake for you.</b></Default>

c0000889
00:35:22.790 --> 00:35:24.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's not what
I'm worried about.</b></Default>

c0000890
00:35:24.210 --> 00:35:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Chicken, then?</b></Default>

c0000891
00:35:25.960 --> 00:35:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales sharply]
The world much be such</b></Default>

c0000892
00:35:28.080 --> 00:35:30.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a blissful place for you.
- What are you saying?</b></Default>

c0000893
00:35:30.750 --> 00:35:33.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What I'm saying is that my
big sister is looking forward</b></Default>

c0000894
00:35:33.630 --> 00:35:35.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to spending Christmas together
with you.</b></Default>

c0000895
00:35:35.550 --> 00:35:37.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like thinking about what
to cook,</b></Default>

c0000896
00:35:37.260 --> 00:35:38.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which store to buy
the cake from,</b></Default>

c0000897
00:35:38.930 --> 00:35:40.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even what kind of clothes
she should wear.</b></Default>

c0000898
00:35:40.760 --> 00:35:42.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000899
00:35:42.520 --> 00:35:44.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Imagining her doing all that
is so cute.</b></Default>

c0000900
00:35:45.350 --> 00:35:47.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you make big sis cry,
I'll never forgive you.</b></Default>

c0000901
00:35:49.480 --> 00:35:51.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We're all finished.
[bot gasping]</b></Default>

c0000902
00:35:54.110 --> 00:35:56.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How's it look?</b></Default>

c0000903
00:35:57.410 --> 00:35:58.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think it looks good.</b></Default>

c0000904
00:35:59.410 --> 00:36:01.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It doesn't look like I
got carried away with it?</b></Default>

c0000905
00:36:01.950 --> 00:36:03.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If we're talking about getting
carried away,</b></Default>

c0000906
00:36:03.790 --> 00:36:06.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that would be more like this.
- But I'm totally not, though!</b></Default>

c0000907
00:36:08.920 --> 00:36:10.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nodoka, I'm sorry to ask this,</b></Default>

c0000908
00:36:10.920 --> 00:36:12.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but do you think you could
take Kaede back home?</b></Default>

c0000909
00:36:12.710 --> 00:36:14.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm? Something come up,
big sis?</b></Default>

c0000910
00:36:14.800 --> 00:36:16.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There's something I
promised Sakuta after this.</b></Default>

c0000911
00:36:17.050 --> 00:36:18.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000912
00:36:19.840 --> 00:36:22.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede, are you okay
to go home without me?</b></Default>

c0000913
00:36:22.760 --> 00:36:26.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother, just how old
do you think I am, exactly?</b></Default>

c0000914
00:36:26.100 --> 00:36:27.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then I guess it'll be fine.</b></Default>

c0000915
00:36:28.020 --> 00:36:30.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's good to see you slowly gain
independence from your brother.</b></Default>

c0000916
00:36:30.730 --> 00:36:32.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is that supposed to be
a dig at me?</b></Default>

c0000917
00:36:32.820 --> 00:36:34.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Toyohama, I want you
to flourish</b></Default>

c0000918
00:36:34.320 --> 00:36:35.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as a sister-obsessed idol.</b></Default>

c0000919
00:36:36.030 --> 00:36:37.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take good care of Mai.</b></Default>

c0000920
00:36:37.530 --> 00:36:39.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? What's that supposed
to mean?</b></Default>

c0000921
00:36:40.070 --> 00:36:42.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[train wheels clacking]</b></Default>

c0000922
00:36:47.370 --> 00:36:50.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, so Mai,
where exactly are we going?</b></Default>

c0000923
00:36:51.130 --> 00:36:52.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Brings back memories, though.</b></Default>

c0000924
00:36:53.000 --> 00:36:55.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We went all the way
to Ogaki together, didn't we?</b></Default>

c0000925
00:36:55.380 --> 00:36:57.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A whole six months ago.</b></Default>

c0000926
00:36:59.760 --> 00:37:02.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Which one of these trains
will take us the furthest?</b></Default>

c0000927
00:37:02.140 --> 00:37:03.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How far are you thinking?</b></Default>

c0000928
00:37:03.470 --> 00:37:05.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Really far.</b></Default>

c0000929
00:37:05.350 --> 00:37:07.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want us to keep
transferring trains</b></Default>

c0000930
00:37:07.230 --> 00:37:09.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and go further than that day.
- Mm.</b></Default>

c0000931
00:37:10.020 --> 00:37:11.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Considering the time,</b></Default>

c0000932
00:37:11.190 --> 00:37:13.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ogaki looks like
the furthest possible.</b></Default>

c0000933
00:37:13.310 --> 00:37:14.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If we ran out of trains,</b></Default>

c0000934
00:37:14.940 --> 00:37:16.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we can spend the night in
a new city.</b></Default>

c0000935
00:37:17.030 --> 00:37:18.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In the same room?</b></Default>

c0000936
00:37:18.360 --> 00:37:20.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sure, if that's
what you'd prefer.</b></Default>

c0000937
00:37:20.610 --> 00:37:22.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- This whole idea sounds like
a dream.</b></Default>

c0000938
00:37:22.820 --> 00:37:25.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And then in the morning
we'll plan to head out again.</b></Default>

c0000939
00:37:25.910 --> 00:37:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll go as far
as we can forever.</b></Default>

c0000940
00:37:27.830 --> 00:37:29.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Very, very far.</b></Default>

c0000941
00:37:29.910 --> 00:37:32.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That sounds like
a seriously good time.</b></Default>

c0000942
00:37:32.130 --> 00:37:34.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But this is all
an elaborate joke, right?</b></Default>

c0000943
00:37:35.670 --> 00:37:37.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I should ask you that.</b></Default>

c0000944
00:37:37.800 --> 00:37:40.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're the one who needs
to stop joking around!</b></Default>

c0000945
00:37:40.340 --> 00:37:42.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't say goodbye to Nodoka
and Kaede like</b></Default>

c0000946
00:37:42.220 --> 00:37:43.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's the last time!
Stop!</b></Default>

c0000947
00:37:43.640 --> 00:37:45.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something's seriously wrong
with you!</b></Default>

c0000948
00:37:45.850 --> 00:37:47.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't just give up
without asking.</b></Default>

c0000949
00:37:47.390 --> 00:37:48.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't decide all by yourself!</b></Default>

c0000950
00:37:50.640 --> 00:37:52.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What am I to you, Sakuta?</b></Default>

c0000951
00:37:52.850 --> 00:37:53.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- My love.</b></Default>

c0000952
00:37:54.440 --> 00:37:55.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then let me bear it, too.</b></Default>

c0000953
00:37:55.940 --> 00:37:58.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The weight of Shoko-chan's life!</b></Default>

c0000954
00:37:58.650 --> 00:38:01.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So please, I'll carry
it with you forever!</b></Default>

c0000955
00:38:01.780 --> 00:38:03.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, I
just need you here
with me!</b></Default>

c0000956
00:38:03.530 --> 00:38:07.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just--just stay right by my side
until Christmas is over!</b></Default>

c0000957
00:38:07.580 --> 00:38:10.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Get on a train with me
and let's go as far as we can!</b></Default>

c0000958
00:38:10.460 --> 00:38:12.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It really would be fun, but...</b></Default>

c0000959
00:38:13.250 --> 00:38:15.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I can't do that.
- Why not?</b></Default>

c0000960
00:38:16.170 --> 00:38:17.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I still have school tomorrow.</b></Default>

c0000961
00:38:17.550 --> 00:38:18.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You can be absent!</b></Default>

c0000962
00:38:19.340 --> 00:38:21.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Besides, you have work
again tomorrow, don't you?</b></Default>

c0000963
00:38:21.590 --> 00:38:23.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't care about that!</b></Default>

c0000964
00:38:23.550 --> 00:38:26.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It means nothing when I think
about losing you, Sakuta!</b></Default>

c0000965
00:38:26.470 --> 00:38:28.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know, I really
do love you, Mai.</b></Default>

c0000966
00:38:29.220 --> 00:38:31.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You always had a full schedule.</b></Default>

c0000967
00:38:31.390 --> 00:38:33.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So it's a shame we couldn't go
on that many dates together.</b></Default>

c0000968
00:38:35.900 --> 00:38:39.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the usual Mai is who
I always wanted to be with.</b></Default>

c0000969
00:38:39.940 --> 00:38:41.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpers]
- And that's the Mai that</b></Default>

c0000970
00:38:41.950 --> 00:38:43.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm completely in love with.</b></Default>

c0000971
00:38:44.110 --> 00:38:45.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Fine, then.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000972
00:38:45.820 --> 00:38:47.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Fine!</b></Default>

c0000973
00:38:47.120 --> 00:38:48.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As long as you stay alive,</b></Default>

c0000974
00:38:48.240 --> 00:38:49.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't care if you hate me!</b></Default>

c0000975
00:38:49.660 --> 00:38:51.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just please stay
with me like this</b></Default>

c0000976
00:38:51.450 --> 00:38:53.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until Christmas is over!</b></Default>

c0000977
00:38:53.410 --> 00:38:55.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then you can hate me
all you want!</b></Default>

c0000978
00:38:55.460 --> 00:38:57.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's impossible.
- What does that mean?</b></Default>

c0000979
00:38:58.380 --> 00:39:00.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There's no way that I
could ever hate you, Mai.</b></Default>

c0000980
00:39:00.420 --> 00:39:01.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [inhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000981
00:39:02.880 --> 00:39:04.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How come?</b></Default>

c0000982
00:39:04.760 --> 00:39:06.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why?</b></Default>

c0000983
00:39:06.180 --> 00:39:08.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000984
00:39:10.970 --> 00:39:13.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll always love you, Mai,
no matter what happens.</b></Default>

c0000985
00:39:14.230 --> 00:39:15.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You liar.</b></Default>

c0000986
00:39:15.600 --> 00:39:17.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I will love you forever.
That's a promise.</b></Default>

c0000987
00:39:17.440 --> 00:39:19.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, you liar.</b></Default>

c0000988
00:39:20.440 --> 00:39:22.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I say that,
but I'm the real liar.</b></Default>

c0000989
00:39:23.360 --> 00:39:25.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really don't want you
to hate me.</b></Default>

c0000990
00:39:26.160 --> 00:39:27.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please don't hate me, okay?</b></Default>

c0000991
00:39:27.700 --> 00:39:30.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000992
00:39:45.220 --> 00:39:47.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hello.
Welcome home, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000993
00:39:47.300 --> 00:39:49.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is Mai staying
at her place again today?</b></Default>

c0000994
00:39:49.220 --> 00:39:50.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh-huh.</b></Default>

c0000995
00:39:50.680 --> 00:39:52.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where's Kaede?</b></Default>

c0000996
00:39:52.140 --> 00:39:53.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She's already resting.</b></Default>

c0000997
00:39:56.020 --> 00:39:57.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shoko-san, listen.</b></Default>

c0000998
00:39:59.900 --> 00:40:01.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shudders]</b></Default>

c0000999
00:40:02.570 --> 00:40:04.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't wanna
make Mai cry like that.</b></Default>

c0001000
00:40:04.360 --> 00:40:05.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was awful.</b></Default>

c0001001
00:40:05.700 --> 00:40:07.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't do it again.</b></Default>

c0001002
00:40:07.570 --> 00:40:08.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't wanna see her like that.</b></Default>

c0001003
00:40:10.160 --> 00:40:12.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why, Shoko-san, I--</b></Default>

c0001004
00:40:12.790 --> 00:40:14.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes? What is it?</b></Default>

c0001005
00:40:15.500 --> 00:40:17.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm sorry, Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0001006
00:40:17.870 --> 00:40:20.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to live.</b></Default>

c0001007
00:40:21.380 --> 00:40:23.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanna stay with Mai forever.</b></Default>

c0001008
00:40:24.090 --> 00:40:25.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To spend the future with her.</b></Default>

c0001009
00:40:26.300 --> 00:40:28.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm the one who needs
to apologize.</b></Default>

c0001010
00:40:28.840 --> 00:40:31.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry I forced you to make
an impossible choice.</b></Default>

c0001011
00:40:32.260 --> 00:40:34.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I'd only found a way
to do better,</b></Default>

c0001012
00:40:34.930 --> 00:40:36.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then I could have avoided
putting you through</b></Default>

c0001013
00:40:36.390 --> 00:40:37.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so much suffering.</b></Default>

c0001014
00:40:37.520 --> 00:40:39.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't say that!</b></Default>

c0001015
00:40:39.270 --> 00:40:41.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001016
00:40:41.230 --> 00:40:43.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's not your fault, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0001017
00:40:43.190 --> 00:40:46.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You put up a valiant effort.
- But I...</b></Default>

c0001018
00:40:46.530 --> 00:40:47.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You answered me properly.</b></Default>

c0001019
00:40:48.030 --> 00:40:49.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpers]</b></Default>

c0001020
00:40:50.780 --> 00:40:53.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's why you need
to go make Mai happy.</b></Default>

c0001021
00:40:54.540 --> 00:40:57.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpering]</b></Default>

c0001022
00:41:05.750 --> 00:41:08.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 24TH</b></Default>

c0001023
00:41:11.050 --> 00:41:13.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, today marks the end
of our happy</b></Default>

c0001024
00:41:13.510 --> 00:41:15.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and somewhat embarrassing days
living together.</b></Default>

c0001025
00:41:19.850 --> 00:41:20.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0001026
00:41:21.060 --> 00:41:23.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- See you later.
[giggles]</b></Default>

c0001027
00:41:23.190 --> 00:41:24.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001028
00:41:25.320 --> 00:41:26.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0001029
00:41:28.110 --> 00:41:29.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be back.</b></Default>

c0001030
00:41:33.950 --> 00:41:35.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Let me ask all of you.</b></Default>

c0001031
00:41:35.490 --> 00:41:37.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you reflect back
on this year,</b></Default>

c0001032
00:41:37.160 --> 00:41:38.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what stands out the most to you?</b></Default>

c0001033
00:41:38.710 --> 00:41:41.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's cold today.
- Yeah, really cold.</b></Default>

c0001034
00:41:41.120 --> 00:41:42.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Crazy, huh?</b></Default>

c0001035
00:41:47.380 --> 00:41:48.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door slides open]</b></Default>

c0001036
00:41:48.970 --> 00:41:50.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Excuse me, Sakuta.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001037
00:41:50.930 --> 00:41:52.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I have a message
to give to you.</b></Default>

c0001038
00:41:53.470 --> 00:41:56.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shoko's mother said that she
wanted you to come visit Shoko.</b></Default>

c0001039
00:42:01.730 --> 00:42:04.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry for all the trouble.
- It's nothing.</b></Default>

c0001040
00:42:04.400 --> 00:42:06.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door hisses]</b></Default>

c0001041
00:42:18.870 --> 00:42:20.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001042
00:42:20.830 --> 00:42:22.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I know that you did your best.</b></Default>

c0001043
00:42:22.830 --> 00:42:24.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You put up a valiant effort.</b></Default>

c0001044
00:42:25.540 --> 00:42:27.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpers]</b></Default>

c0001045
00:42:27.090 --> 00:42:29.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She really is amazing.</b></Default>

c0001046
00:42:31.420 --> 00:42:34.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even now Makinohara
is doing her best.</b></Default>

c0001047
00:42:37.640 --> 00:42:38.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone receiver clicks]</b></Default>

c0001048
00:42:39.560 --> 00:42:40.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's me.</b></Default>

c0001049
00:42:41.310 --> 00:42:42.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai.</b></Default>

c0001050
00:42:43.140 --> 00:42:45.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I--
- Last night, I had a dream.</b></Default>

c0001051
00:42:46.480 --> 00:42:48.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We were going to the shrine
for New Year's.</b></Default>

c0001052
00:42:49.440 --> 00:42:51.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you wouldn't stop bragging
about how you swore</b></Default>

c0001053
00:42:51.740 --> 00:42:54.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the gods that you were going
to make me happy no matter what.</b></Default>

c0001054
00:42:55.030 --> 00:42:56.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That does sound like something
I'd say.</b></Default>

c0001055
00:42:57.450 --> 00:42:58.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes.</b></Default>

c0001056
00:42:58.580 --> 00:42:59.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's just like you to lie</b></Default>

c0001057
00:42:59.830 --> 00:43:01.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in my dreams like
in real life.</b></Default>

c0001058
00:43:01.200 --> 00:43:02.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0001059
00:43:02.960 --> 00:43:05.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, I will never let
myself forget about you.</b></Default>

c0001060
00:43:06.380 --> 00:43:08.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You will be a part
of me forever.</b></Default>

c0001061
00:43:09.090 --> 00:43:11.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
Mai, I--listen.</b></Default>

c0001062
00:43:11.340 --> 00:43:12.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[coin clinks]</b></Default>

c0001063
00:43:12.550 --> 00:43:15.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone beeps]</b></Default>

c0001064
00:43:15.470 --> 00:43:16.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0001065
00:43:18.260 --> 00:43:19.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone hangs on receiver]</b></Default>

c0001066
00:43:20.430 --> 00:43:23.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0001067
00:43:24.890 --> 00:43:27.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic piano music]</b></Default>

c0001068
00:43:27.860 --> 00:43:34.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001069
00:44:04.430 --> 00:44:06.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[engine revving]
[tires squealing]</b></Default>

c0001070
00:44:09.190 --> 00:44:10.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001071
00:44:21.120 --> 00:44:24.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why didn't it--is it supposed
to be at the next stoplight?</b></Default>

c0001072
00:44:24.160 --> 00:44:26.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You can see the sea candle.
So pretty.</b></Default>

c0001073
00:44:26.870 --> 00:44:32.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001074
00:44:33.000 --> 00:44:34.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001075
00:44:35.010 --> 00:44:37.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How about the illumination
at Enoshima?</b></Default>

c0001076
00:44:37.170 --> 00:44:38.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Please go with me.</b></Default>

c0001077
00:44:38.720 --> 00:44:41.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's watch the illumination
in Enoshima together.</b></Default>

c0001078
00:44:41.720 --> 00:44:43.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001079
00:44:43.350 --> 00:44:47.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could it be that from
the very beginning, Shoko-san...</b></Default>

c0001080
00:44:47.730 --> 00:44:50.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0001081
00:44:50.730 --> 00:44:52.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's crazy!</b></Default>

c0001082
00:44:52.320 --> 00:44:54.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shoko-san is out of her mind!</b></Default>

c0001083
00:44:54.940 --> 00:44:56.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She knew that I would go to Mai.</b></Default>

c0001084
00:44:56.650 --> 00:44:58.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She knew from the beginning!</b></Default>

c0001085
00:44:58.490 --> 00:44:59.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why she said--</b></Default>

c0001086
00:45:00.030 --> 00:45:02.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- At 6:00 o'clock p.m. on
the 24th,</b></Default>

c0001087
00:45:02.530 --> 00:45:04.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be at the entrance
to Bentembashi</b></Default>

c0001088
00:45:04.740 --> 00:45:06.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>right by the dragon lantern.</b></Default>

c0001089
00:45:06.370 --> 00:45:08.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Because she knew!</b></Default>

c0001090
00:45:08.210 --> 00:45:10.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She knew I would never
show up there!</b></Default>

c0001091
00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:12.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Everything should be resolved
very soon,</b></Default>

c0001092
00:45:12.380 --> 00:45:14.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by the time Christmas comes
to an end.</b></Default>

c0001093
00:45:14.130 --> 00:45:16.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I'd only found a way
to do better.</b></Default>

c0001094
00:45:16.550 --> 00:45:18.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See you later.
[giggles]</b></Default>

c0001095
00:45:18.670 --> 00:45:20.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why would you do all that?</b></Default>

c0001096
00:45:20.640 --> 00:45:23.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something has to be seriously
wrong with your mind, Shoko-san!</b></Default>

c0001097
00:45:23.640 --> 00:45:24.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0001098
00:45:24.890 --> 00:45:26.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, watch out!
That's dangerous!</b></Default>

c0001099
00:45:28.390 --> 00:45:30.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- This can't be how it ends!</b></Default>

c0001100
00:45:30.480 --> 00:45:33.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm begging! Let me get there
before it's too late!</b></Default>

c0001101
00:45:33.690 --> 00:45:35.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[tires squealing]</b></Default>

c0001102
00:45:37.940 --> 00:45:38.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, no!</b></Default>

c0001103
00:45:49.290 --> 00:45:50.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta!</b></Default>

c0001104
00:45:52.960 --> 00:45:54.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0001105
00:45:54.840 --> 00:45:56.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[tires squealing]</b></Default>

c0001106
00:45:56.210 --> 00:45:58.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasping]</b></Default>

c0001107
00:46:00.170 --> 00:46:01.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-
What the--</b></Default>

c0001108
00:46:02.680 --> 00:46:05.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groaning]</b></Default>

c0001109
00:46:07.350 --> 00:46:09.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001110
00:46:11.020 --> 00:46:12.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0001111
00:46:14.690 --> 00:46:15.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001112
00:46:17.320 --> 00:46:19.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0001113
00:46:21.280 --> 00:46:22.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shuddering]</b></Default>

c0001114
00:46:22.780 --> 00:46:25.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0001115
00:46:41.590 --> 00:46:43.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- My daughter. Mai.</b></Default>

c0001116
00:46:44.430 --> 00:46:46.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is she really...</b></Default>

c0001117
00:46:46.930 --> 00:46:48.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We did everything
that we could.</b></Default>

c0001118
00:46:48.600 --> 00:46:50.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so sorry.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001119
00:46:50.600 --> 00:46:53.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

c0001120
00:46:53.100 --> 00:46:56.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My... my girl.</b></Default>

c0001121
00:46:57.110 --> 00:46:58.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Give her back!</b></Default>

c0001122
00:46:58.980 --> 00:47:02.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]
Give her back!</b></Default>

c0001123
00:47:03.070 --> 00:47:06.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wailing]</b></Default>

c0001124
00:47:21.510 --> 00:47:22.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why?</b></Default>

c0001125
00:47:22.920 --> 00:47:24.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why?</b></Default>

c0001126
00:47:24.380 --> 00:47:26.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why didn't you protect
my big sister like you</b></Default>

c0001127
00:47:26.760 --> 00:47:28.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were supposed to, Sakuta?</b></Default>

c0001128
00:47:29.720 --> 00:47:30.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How come?</b></Default>

c0001129
00:47:31.930 --> 00:47:35.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why did she--why her?</b></Default>

c0001130
00:47:36.230 --> 00:47:38.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0001131
00:47:39.070 --> 00:47:40.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0001132
00:47:40.820 --> 00:47:41.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0001133
00:47:42.280 --> 00:47:43.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I...</b></Default>

c0001134
00:47:43.940 --> 00:47:44.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was the one that died...</b></Default>

c0001135
00:47:57.790 --> 00:47:59.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaking]</b></Default>

c0001136
00:48:00.840 --> 00:48:02.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I
see.</b></Default>

c0001137
00:48:02.510 --> 00:48:03.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's right.</b></Default>

c0001138
00:48:04.420 --> 00:48:07.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since my life was saved,
that means Shoko-san...</b></Default>

c0001139
00:48:08.470 --> 00:48:09.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001140
00:48:10.760 --> 00:48:11.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001141
00:48:12.890 --> 00:48:14.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0001142
00:48:15.060 --> 00:48:16.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001143
00:48:17.350 --> 00:48:18.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the end...</b></Default>

c0001144
00:48:20.020 --> 00:48:21.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't protect anyone.</b></Default>

c0001145
00:48:21.820 --> 00:48:23.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001146
00:48:26.860 --> 00:48:29.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell ringing]</b></Default>

c0001147
00:48:31.780 --> 00:48:33.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cat purring]</b></Default>

c0001148
00:48:33.370 --> 00:48:34.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cat meows]</b></Default>

c0001149
00:48:35.040 --> 00:48:36.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The door's unlocked.</b></Default>

c0001150
00:48:36.240 --> 00:48:37.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 25TH</b></Default>

c0001151
00:48:38.080 --> 00:48:40.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, you here?
We're coming in!</b></Default>

c0001152
00:48:44.300 --> 00:48:46.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001153
00:48:48.050 --> 00:48:49.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We saw the accident on
the news.</b></Default>

c0001154
00:48:49.930 --> 00:48:51.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We've been trying
to call you nonstop.</b></Default>

c0001155
00:48:52.510 --> 00:48:54.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-
Sorry to worry you.</b></Default>

c0001156
00:48:54.640 --> 00:48:55.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001157
00:48:57.100 --> 00:48:59.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You have four new messages.</b></Default>

c0001158
00:48:59.810 --> 00:49:01.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>First message.</b></Default>

c0001159
00:49:01.650 --> 00:49:03.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>7:03 a.m.</b></Default>

c0001160
00:49:03.650 --> 00:49:05.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother, it's not real,
right?</b></Default>

c0001161
00:49:06.070 --> 00:49:07.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me it's a lie!</b></Default>

c0001162
00:49:07.530 --> 00:49:09.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no way
that could happen to Mai!</b></Default>

c0001163
00:49:09.530 --> 00:49:12.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hand me the phone.
Sakuta, if you get this message,</b></Default>

c0001164
00:49:12.530 --> 00:49:13.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>please call us.</b></Default>

c0001165
00:49:13.990 --> 00:49:16.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You can call your family on
the way, okay?</b></Default>

c0001166
00:49:16.080 --> 00:49:17.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0001167
00:49:18.040 --> 00:49:19.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Where?</b></Default>

c0001168
00:49:19.460 --> 00:49:21.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Photos and videos
of the accident scene</b></Default>

c0001169
00:49:21.210 --> 00:49:23.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are making the rounds
on social media now.</b></Default>

c0001170
00:49:23.540 --> 00:49:25.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You showed up in a few
of them, too.</b></Default>

c0001171
00:49:25.710 --> 00:49:27.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.</b></Default>

c0001172
00:49:27.210 --> 00:49:29.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You should come stay over
at my place for a while.</b></Default>

c0001173
00:49:29.720 --> 00:49:32.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I predict the media's going
to have this place surrounded.</b></Default>

c0001174
00:49:35.620 --> 00:49:38.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>THE LATE MAI SAKURAJIMA
MEMORIAL SERVICE</b></Default>

c0001175
00:49:41.410 --> 00:49:44.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>THE LATE MAI SAKURAJIMA
FUNERAL SERVICE</b></Default>

c0001176
00:49:47.250 --> 00:49:48.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 28TH</b></Default>

c0001177
00:49:48.280 --> 00:49:50.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm here at a funeral home
in Tokyo.</b></Default>

c0001178
00:49:51.070 --> 00:49:53.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the rain that started
to fall early afternoon,</b></Default>

c0001179
00:49:53.740 --> 00:49:57.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Actress Mai Sakurajima's funeral
service is currently being held.</b></Default>

c0001180
00:49:57.370 --> 00:49:59.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Many of our viewers may
already be aware</b></Default>

c0001181
00:49:59.710 --> 00:50:01.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the situation,
but four days ago,</b></Default>

c0001182
00:50:01.790 --> 00:50:03.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on December the 24th,</b></Default>

c0001183
00:50:03.580 --> 00:50:06.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Actress Mai Sakurajima was
involved in a traffic accident</b></Default>

c0001184
00:50:06.750 --> 00:50:07.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and has passed away.</b></Default>

c0001185
00:50:07.960 --> 00:50:09.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is real, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0001186
00:50:09.720 --> 00:50:12.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Actually, the day before
the accident, I--</b></Default>

c0001187
00:50:12.590 --> 00:50:14.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I've never done something
like this.</b></Default>

c0001188
00:50:14.760 --> 00:50:17.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So there's a lot
I'm not confident about.</b></Default>

c0001189
00:50:17.140 --> 00:50:20.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But Mai, this boy we're
talking about must be completely</b></Default>

c0001190
00:50:20.100 --> 00:50:21.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>wrapped around your finger,
right?</b></Default>

c0001191
00:50:21.600 --> 00:50:23.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And just what kind of person
do you think I am?</b></Default>

c0001192
00:50:24.060 --> 00:50:25.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though I suppose I do have
the upper hand.</b></Default>

c0001193
00:50:25.860 --> 00:50:27.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [laughs]
I knew it.</b></Default>

c0001194
00:50:27.400 --> 00:50:30.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But still, I'm sure I love him
more than he loves me.</b></Default>

c0001195
00:50:30.280 --> 00:50:32.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? Is that okay to say?</b></Default>

c0001196
00:50:32.450 --> 00:50:34.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He'll probably end up
seeing this, too, you know.</b></Default>

c0001197
00:50:35.070 --> 00:50:36.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001198
00:50:36.580 --> 00:50:38.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

c0001199
00:50:41.080 --> 00:50:43.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[children laughing]</b></Default>

c0001200
00:50:50.420 --> 00:50:51.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please save her.</b></Default>

c0001201
00:50:53.800 --> 00:50:55.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please save her.</b></Default>

c0001202
00:50:57.390 --> 00:50:58.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone.</b></Default>

c0001203
00:50:59.270 --> 00:51:00.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please save Mai.</b></Default>

c0001204
00:51:08.020 --> 00:51:09.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It doesn't matter who.</b></Default>

c0001205
00:51:17.070 --> 00:51:19.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001206
00:51:21.330 --> 00:51:23.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please save Mai.</b></Default>

c0001207
00:51:24.120 --> 00:51:25.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Somehow, please!</b></Default>

c0001208
00:51:26.580 --> 00:51:28.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I beg you!
[sniffles]</b></Default>

c0001209
00:51:28.750 --> 00:51:29.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please!</b></Default>

c0001210
00:51:29.920 --> 00:51:32.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0001211
00:51:34.550 --> 00:51:36.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Please stand up, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0001212
00:51:36.640 --> 00:51:37.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001213
00:51:41.600 --> 00:51:43.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Saving Mai is supposed
to be your job.</b></Default>

c0001214
00:51:43.930 --> 00:51:46.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't it, Sakuta?
Or am I wrong?</b></Default>

c0001215
00:51:47.190 --> 00:51:50.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How? How are you still here,
Shoko-san?</b></Default>

c0001216
00:51:50.650 --> 00:51:52.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.</b></Default>

c0001217
00:51:52.110 --> 00:51:54.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't know about it yet, do
you?</b></Default>

c0001218
00:51:56.280 --> 00:51:58.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here inside my chest.</b></Default>

c0001219
00:51:58.490 --> 00:52:00.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The heart that's beating on
is Mai's.</b></Default>

c0001220
00:52:00.490 --> 00:52:01.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?</b></Default>

c0001221
00:52:01.870 --> 00:52:04.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- This information
was never made public.</b></Default>

c0001222
00:52:04.410 --> 00:52:06.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that night after
the accident,</b></Default>

c0001223
00:52:06.500 --> 00:52:09.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai coincidentally became
my donor instead.</b></Default>

c0001224
00:52:09.500 --> 00:52:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wait, she had a donor card,
too?</b></Default>

c0001225
00:52:11.590 --> 00:52:13.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes.
- But then,</b></Default>

c0001226
00:52:13.880 --> 00:52:15.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that would mean
the future's different.</b></Default>

c0001227
00:52:15.720 --> 00:52:16.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Come on, now.</b></Default>

c0001228
00:52:17.050 --> 00:52:18.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go save Mai.</b></Default>

c0001229
00:52:18.760 --> 00:52:20.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What do you mean?
Where to?</b></Default>

c0001230
00:52:20.510 --> 00:52:22.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Back to the past, of course.</b></Default>

c0001231
00:52:22.350 --> 00:52:24.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But that would be--
- It's possible.</b></Default>

c0001232
00:52:24.980 --> 00:52:26.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can leave it to me.</b></Default>

c0001233
00:52:32.150 --> 00:52:34.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no need to worry.
You can relax.</b></Default>

c0001234
00:52:34.650 --> 00:52:36.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since today is Mai's
funeral service,</b></Default>

c0001235
00:52:36.650 --> 00:52:38.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>nobody's going to be here.</b></Default>

c0001236
00:52:38.200 --> 00:52:40.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why the nurse's office?</b></Default>

c0001237
00:52:40.200 --> 00:52:43.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- A bed is required
to return to the past.</b></Default>

c0001238
00:52:47.330 --> 00:52:48.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0001239
00:52:48.580 --> 00:52:50.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gagging]</b></Default>

c0001240
00:52:50.130 --> 00:52:53.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shoko-san, is this--
- It's plum soda for adults.</b></Default>

c0001241
00:52:53.380 --> 00:52:54.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0001242
00:52:55.590 --> 00:52:58.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, you already know
it's possible, don't you?</b></Default>

c0001243
00:52:58.880 --> 00:53:01.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The future actually exists
pretty close by.</b></Default>

c0001244
00:53:01.640 --> 00:53:03.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I'm also from the future.</b></Default>

c0001245
00:53:03.390 --> 00:53:04.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But in your case,</b></Default>

c0001246
00:53:04.930 --> 00:53:06.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't time travel something
you're able to do as part</b></Default>

c0001247
00:53:06.980 --> 00:53:08.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of your puberty syndrome?</b></Default>

c0001248
00:53:08.270 --> 00:53:09.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes.</b></Default>

c0001249
00:53:10.190 --> 00:53:12.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The entire reason my younger
self developed puberty syndrome</b></Default>

c0001250
00:53:12.860 --> 00:53:14.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the first place
was her anxiety</b></Default>

c0001251
00:53:14.730 --> 00:53:15.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about the future.</b></Default>

c0001252
00:53:16.150 --> 00:53:17.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bed creaks]</b></Default>

c0001253
00:53:17.610 --> 00:53:19.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But this moment that
you're experiencing now</b></Default>

c0001254
00:53:19.570 --> 00:53:21.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where you and I are speaking
like this wouldn't</b></Default>

c0001255
00:53:21.700 --> 00:53:23.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>be called the present.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0001256
00:53:24.200 --> 00:53:26.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And you're the one
that caused this.</b></Default>

c0001257
00:53:26.370 --> 00:53:28.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you have any clue why
that might be?</b></Default>

c0001258
00:53:28.250 --> 00:53:29.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

c0001259
00:53:29.960 --> 00:53:32.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's the same thing that
happened with my younger self.</b></Default>

c0001260
00:53:32.540 --> 00:53:34.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There was a time
when you refused</b></Default>

c0001261
00:53:34.130 --> 00:53:35.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your own future, wasn't there?</b></Default>

c0001262
00:53:36.300 --> 00:53:38.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I want you to choose a future
with me, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0001263
00:53:39.050 --> 00:53:42.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How come?
- I want to live.</b></Default>

c0001264
00:53:42.930 --> 00:53:44.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0001265
00:53:44.760 --> 00:53:47.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It looks like you have
a pretty good idea of when.</b></Default>

c0001266
00:53:47.100 --> 00:53:48.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I mean...</b></Default>

c0001267
00:53:48.680 --> 00:53:51.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You should properly
acknowledge what you're feeling.</b></Default>

c0001268
00:53:51.400 --> 00:53:53.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stop trying to ignore
the weak self within you</b></Default>

c0001269
00:53:53.770 --> 00:53:56.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that refused your own future.
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0001270
00:53:56.570 --> 00:53:58.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Just have faith in
that weakness.</b></Default>

c0001271
00:53:58.650 --> 00:54:01.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the first step to seeing
this moment as the future.</b></Default>

c0001272
00:54:02.030 --> 00:54:03.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we're in the future,</b></Default>

c0001273
00:54:03.950 --> 00:54:06.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then you can travel
to the present, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0001274
00:54:06.740 --> 00:54:09.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it would even be possible
to save Mai.</b></Default>

c0001275
00:54:10.410 --> 00:54:12.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shoko-san.
- What is it?</b></Default>

c0001276
00:54:13.750 --> 00:54:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I want so badly
to make Mai happy.</b></Default>

c0001277
00:54:16.340 --> 00:54:18.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And that's doable.</b></Default>

c0001278
00:54:18.630 --> 00:54:20.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's why before
I do anything,</b></Default>

c0001279
00:54:20.800 --> 00:54:22.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there's something I need
to tell you.</b></Default>

c0001280
00:54:23.180 --> 00:54:25.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I also really, really want you
to stay alive.</b></Default>

c0001281
00:54:25.510 --> 00:54:26.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes.</b></Default>

c0001282
00:54:26.850 --> 00:54:29.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I hope and pray for it.</b></Default>

c0001283
00:54:29.480 --> 00:54:31.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I know you do.</b></Default>

c0001284
00:54:31.190 --> 00:54:32.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But I'm not a doctor.</b></Default>

c0001285
00:54:32.730 --> 00:54:34.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no special powers,
either.</b></Default>

c0001286
00:54:35.730 --> 00:54:39.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It takes everything in me just
to make Mai happy.</b></Default>

c0001287
00:54:41.240 --> 00:54:44.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And even then I couldn't
handle that one single job.</b></Default>

c0001288
00:54:44.950 --> 00:54:47.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why--that's why,
Shoko-san...</b></Default>

c0001289
00:54:47.450 --> 00:54:48.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Go on.</b></Default>

c0001290
00:54:49.750 --> 00:54:52.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- As much as I wish I could,
I just can't help you.</b></Default>

c0001291
00:54:54.330 --> 00:54:56.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And that's exactly how
it should be.</b></Default>

c0001292
00:54:57.710 --> 00:55:00.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sniffles]</b></Default>

c0001293
00:55:03.470 --> 00:55:06.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why am I--I already decided
on this.</b></Default>

c0001294
00:55:06.640 --> 00:55:07.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0001295
00:55:09.220 --> 00:55:11.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0001296
00:55:12.520 --> 00:55:13.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001297
00:55:15.730 --> 00:55:17.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-
It appears the dose
I snuck in earlier has begun</b></Default>

c0001298
00:55:17.940 --> 00:55:19.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to take effect.</b></Default>

c0001299
00:55:19.730 --> 00:55:21.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In order to send you
to the present,</b></Default>

c0001300
00:55:21.940 --> 00:55:24.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just needed to break you away
from the ordinary logic</b></Default>

c0001301
00:55:24.740 --> 00:55:27.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that keeps you from trying
to perceive current time.</b></Default>

c0001302
00:55:27.990 --> 00:55:30.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The only place where you can
truly toss the ordinary aside</b></Default>

c0001303
00:55:31.080 --> 00:55:32.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is a dream.</b></Default>

c0001304
