<Default><b>- I'm from the future,
but only four days.</b></Default>

c0001470
01:02:03.720 --> 01:02:04.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.</b></Default>

c0001471
01:02:04.930 --> 01:02:06.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I got the voicemail
from Sakuta,</b></Default>

c0001472
01:02:06.770 --> 01:02:08.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he said the future version
of him was around,</b></Default>

c0001473
01:02:08.770 --> 01:02:10.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I got my hopes up.</b></Default>

c0001474
01:02:10.270 --> 01:02:12.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you give me enough time,
I will grow up,</b></Default>

c0001475
01:02:12.980 --> 01:02:14.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so please wait until then.
- [chuckles]</b></Default>

c0001476
01:02:16.610 --> 01:02:18.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to get going now.</b></Default>

c0001477
01:02:18.280 --> 01:02:20.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta and I made plans
for a date tonight.</b></Default>

c0001478
01:02:20.610 --> 01:02:21.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0001479
01:02:21.820 --> 01:02:23.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on, Mai!</b></Default>

c0001480
01:02:23.450 --> 01:02:24.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah, let go of me!</b></Default>

c0001481
01:02:24.870 --> 01:02:25.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's gonna be all right!</b></Default>

c0001482
01:02:25.910 --> 01:02:27.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How can it be all right?</b></Default>

c0001483
01:02:27.450 --> 01:02:28.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001484
01:02:28.750 --> 01:02:30.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If Sakuta knows what
I'm planning,</b></Default>

c0001485
01:02:30.540 --> 01:02:32.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he's just going
to try even harder</b></Default>

c0001486
01:02:32.080 --> 01:02:34.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to sacrifice himself!
It's obvious!</b></Default>

c0001487
01:02:34.500 --> 01:02:36.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He'll think he should be
in that accident.</b></Default>

c0001488
01:02:36.380 --> 01:02:37.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know it.</b></Default>

c0001489
01:02:38.420 --> 01:02:40.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If he chooses to avoid that fate
and keep living,</b></Default>

c0001490
01:02:41.050 --> 01:02:43.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he'll see it as robbing
Shoko-chan of her future!</b></Default>

c0001491
01:02:44.220 --> 01:02:47.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why if I don't go,
Sakuta's going to die!</b></Default>

c0001492
01:02:47.100 --> 01:02:48.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
- Mai, you can't go.</b></Default>

c0001493
01:02:48.770 --> 01:02:50.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You need to stay here, please.</b></Default>

c0001494
01:02:51.310 --> 01:02:53.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm begging you.</b></Default>

c0001495
01:02:54.770 --> 01:02:56.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't take it anymore, Mai.</b></Default>

c0001496
01:02:56.730 --> 01:02:58.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A world without you in it.</b></Default>

c0001497
01:02:59.820 --> 01:03:01.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't worry about me.</b></Default>

c0001498
01:03:01.700 --> 01:03:03.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll take care of my own self.</b></Default>

c0001499
01:03:04.860 --> 01:03:06.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And you're fine with that?</b></Default>

c0001500
01:03:07.370 --> 01:03:08.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's my choice.</b></Default>

c0001501
01:03:08.950 --> 01:03:10.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I want you to wait it out.</b></Default>

c0001502
01:03:11.450 --> 01:03:13.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is it gonna be all right?</b></Default>

c0001503
01:03:13.710 --> 01:03:15.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Knowing me, I'll be a mess.</b></Default>

c0001504
01:03:15.920 --> 01:03:18.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll come home
in shambles crying.</b></Default>

c0001505
01:03:18.590 --> 01:03:21.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So please hug me like this when
the time comes.</b></Default>

c0001506
01:03:21.720 --> 01:03:24.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do that and I promise I
will make you happy, Mai.</b></Default>

c0001507
01:03:24.930 --> 01:03:26.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0001508
01:03:26.220 --> 01:03:27.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I will.</b></Default>

c0001509
01:03:27.970 --> 01:03:30.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thank you so much.</b></Default>

c0001510
01:03:30.720 --> 01:03:32.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But still,
you're making one mistake.</b></Default>

c0001511
01:03:37.230 --> 01:03:39.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thing is, I don't exactly
need you to make me happy.</b></Default>

c0001512
01:03:40.070 --> 01:03:40.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That isn't the point.</b></Default>

c0001513
01:03:41.030 --> 01:03:42.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?</b></Default>

c0001514
01:03:42.320 --> 01:03:44.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The point is
to be happy together.</b></Default>

c0001515
01:03:44.280 --> 01:03:46.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That means you and me, okay?</b></Default>

c0001516
01:03:48.740 --> 01:03:51.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, man. I really can't
win against you, can I?</b></Default>

c0001517
01:03:52.330 --> 01:03:54.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll wait for you, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0001518
01:03:55.540 --> 01:03:58.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[distant Christmas
music playing]</b></Default>

c0001519
01:03:58.420 --> 01:04:05.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001520
01:04:05.880 --> 01:04:07.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001521
01:04:12.390 --> 01:04:13.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0001522
01:04:15.640 --> 01:04:17.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to make you wait.</b></Default>

c0001523
01:04:17.270 --> 01:04:18.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I haven't been here long.</b></Default>

c0001524
01:04:18.770 --> 01:04:20.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides, it's still before
the meeting time.</b></Default>

c0001525
01:04:20.730 --> 01:04:22.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In any case,</b></Default>

c0001526
01:04:22.320 --> 01:04:24.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you sure have a unique
interpretation of dressing up.</b></Default>

c0001527
01:04:24.690 --> 01:04:26.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I've been wearing it all day.</b></Default>

c0001528
01:04:26.490 --> 01:04:28.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It feels like it's just
a part of me at this point.</b></Default>

c0001529
01:04:29.280 --> 01:04:30.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0001530
01:04:31.030 --> 01:04:32.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This can only mean
that I failed.</b></Default>

c0001531
01:04:32.910 --> 01:04:35.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You didn't fail in
the slightest.</b></Default>

c0001532
01:04:35.160 --> 01:04:37.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't be here now
if it weren't for you.</b></Default>

c0001533
01:04:37.580 --> 01:04:39.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As the future me.</b></Default>

c0001534
01:04:40.710 --> 01:04:43.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, hold hands with me.</b></Default>

c0001535
01:04:43.300 --> 01:04:44.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [chuckles]</b></Default>

c0001536
01:04:49.640 --> 01:04:51.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's a little embarrassing.</b></Default>

c0001537
01:04:56.940 --> 01:05:00.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shoko-san, I'm going to carry
it all with me.</b></Default>

c0001538
01:05:00.610 --> 01:05:04.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The time I spent with you,
the memories--everything.</b></Default>

c0001539
01:05:05.110 --> 01:05:07.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll take every last bit
of what you shared with me</b></Default>

c0001540
01:05:07.200 --> 01:05:08.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the future.</b></Default>

c0001541
01:05:08.780 --> 01:05:10.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [chuckles]</b></Default>

c0001542
01:05:11.240 --> 01:05:15.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, why do you think it is
that people can forget all sorts</b></Default>

c0001543
01:05:15.120 --> 01:05:16.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of things that happened
in their lives?</b></Default>

c0001544
01:05:16.910 --> 01:05:18.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It doesn't matter
'cause I won't.</b></Default>

c0001545
01:05:18.540 --> 01:05:20.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think I know why.</b></Default>

c0001546
01:05:20.580 --> 01:05:23.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They can only tolerate painful
memories for so long.</b></Default>

c0001547
01:05:23.380 --> 01:05:25.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Letting go becomes necessary.</b></Default>

c0001548
01:05:25.710 --> 01:05:28.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In that case, I don't see any
reason why I would ever forget</b></Default>

c0001549
01:05:28.550 --> 01:05:30.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about you.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0001550
01:05:30.970 --> 01:05:32.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Because it's bitter sweet
to me.</b></Default>

c0001551
01:05:32.800 --> 01:05:35.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, it's the memory
of my first love.</b></Default>

c0001552
01:05:35.220 --> 01:05:36.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no need to forget.</b></Default>

c0001553
01:05:36.930 --> 01:05:37.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001554
01:05:38.060 --> 01:05:39.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really, now.</b></Default>

c0001555
01:05:39.600 --> 01:05:41.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's that twisted personality
of yours.</b></Default>

c0001556
01:05:43.400 --> 01:05:45.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I need to get going now.</b></Default>

c0001557
01:05:45.610 --> 01:05:46.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Okay.</b></Default>

c0001558
01:05:55.240 --> 01:05:57.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Goodbye, Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0001559
01:05:57.620 --> 01:06:00.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
Bye-bye, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0001560
01:06:06.630 --> 01:06:08.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- At the quantum level,</b></Default>

c0001561
01:06:08.210 --> 01:06:10.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my two selves will never be able
to meet.</b></Default>

c0001562
01:06:10.630 --> 01:06:14.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that should also mean that
as long as I'm not recognized,</b></Default>

c0001563
01:06:14.140 --> 01:06:15.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we can exist simultaneously.</b></Default>

c0001564
01:06:16.430 --> 01:06:19.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0001565
01:06:20.520 --> 01:06:22.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[tires squealing]
[car horns honking]</b></Default>

c0001566
01:06:22.190 --> 01:06:24.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [breathing heavily]
- Sakuta, no!</b></Default>

c0001567
01:06:27.650 --> 01:06:28.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0001568
01:06:28.570 --> 01:06:29.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0001569
01:06:33.490 --> 01:06:34.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crashing]</b></Default>

c0001570
01:06:34.990 --> 01:06:36.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[tires squealing]
[all gasping]</b></Default>

c0001571
01:06:36.490 --> 01:06:38.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0001572
01:06:39.290 --> 01:06:40.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What the--</b></Default>

c0001573
01:06:43.080 --> 01:06:45.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groaning]
Did I...</b></Default>

c0001574
01:06:49.130 --> 01:06:51.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.
That's what happens.</b></Default>

c0001575
01:06:52.470 --> 01:06:54.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You okay?
Are you hurt?</b></Default>

c0001576
01:06:54.800 --> 01:06:57.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey!
- Don't worry. I'm okay.</b></Default>

c0001577
01:06:59.350 --> 01:07:00.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001578
01:07:06.230 --> 01:07:07.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0001579
01:07:10.570 --> 01:07:11.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I took it away from her.</b></Default>

c0001580
01:07:12.990 --> 01:07:14.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makinohara's future.</b></Default>

c0001581
01:07:16.410 --> 01:07:19.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But there was no other way
for me.</b></Default>

c0001582
01:07:20.080 --> 01:07:21.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There wasn't.</b></Default>

c0001583
01:07:24.620 --> 01:07:27.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic music]</b></Default>

c0001584
01:07:27.590 --> 01:07:34.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001585
01:07:58.700 --> 01:07:59.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sniffles]</b></Default>

c0001586
01:08:00.660 --> 01:08:02.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm home.</b></Default>

c0001587
01:08:02.950 --> 01:08:04.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Welcome back.</b></Default>

c0001588
01:08:04.830 --> 01:08:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001589
01:08:26.100 --> 01:08:27.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's already 10:00.
You should get up.</b></Default>

c0001590
01:08:28.400 --> 01:08:30.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I know.
I'm awake.</b></Default>

c0001591
01:08:30.150 --> 01:08:32.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Go eat your breakfast before
it gets cold, okay?</b></Default>

c0001592
01:08:32.730 --> 01:08:34.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to head to school.</b></Default>

c0001593
01:08:34.440 --> 01:08:36.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Isn't it winter break
right now, though?</b></Default>

c0001594
01:08:36.820 --> 01:08:39.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I was absent yesterday because
of work.</b></Default>

c0001595
01:08:39.120 --> 01:08:40.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need to go pick up
my report card.</b></Default>

c0001596
01:08:40.870 --> 01:08:42.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then I'll go with you.</b></Default>

c0001597
01:08:47.040 --> 01:08:47.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Futaba.</b></Default>

c0001598
01:08:48.920 --> 01:08:50.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0001599
01:08:53.670 --> 01:08:54.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001600
01:08:55.050 --> 01:08:56.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, whoa, there.</b></Default>

c0001601
01:08:56.670 --> 01:08:57.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You all right?</b></Default>

c0001602
01:08:58.010 --> 01:08:59.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm not.</b></Default>

c0001603
01:08:59.390 --> 01:09:00.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Futaba.</b></Default>

c0001604
01:09:00.890 --> 01:09:02.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm not all right!</b></Default>

c0001605
01:09:03.510 --> 01:09:05.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm sorry
for making you worry.</b></Default>

c0001606
01:09:06.890 --> 01:09:08.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm not all right.</b></Default>

c0001607
01:09:08.770 --> 01:09:11.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really thought I
would never see you again.</b></Default>

c0001608
01:09:11.400 --> 01:09:13.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad I was wrong.</b></Default>

c0001609
01:09:13.150 --> 01:09:14.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That you're still alive.</b></Default>

c0001610
01:09:15.900 --> 01:09:18.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yesterday, what happened?</b></Default>

c0001611
01:09:18.280 --> 01:09:20.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So much, to be honest.</b></Default>

c0001612
01:09:20.110 --> 01:09:21.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where do I even begin?</b></Default>

c0001613
01:09:21.950 --> 01:09:24.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just know there was something
that needed to be done</b></Default>

c0001614
01:09:24.870 --> 01:09:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I did it.</b></Default>

c0001615
01:09:30.330 --> 01:09:33.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, uh, which one are you?</b></Default>

c0001616
01:09:33.250 --> 01:09:34.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Both of them.</b></Default>

c0001617
01:09:34.550 --> 01:09:35.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because we fused.</b></Default>

c0001618
01:09:36.010 --> 01:09:37.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't flipping get it.</b></Default>

c0001619
01:09:37.590 --> 01:09:39.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry I put you through all
of that.</b></Default>

c0001620
01:09:39.760 --> 01:09:42.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really appreciate what you
did, Koga.</b></Default>

c0001621
01:09:43.930 --> 01:09:45.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Here you go.</b></Default>

c0001622
01:09:45.180 --> 01:09:47.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Some souvenirs from Grandma.</b></Default>

c0001623
01:09:47.100 --> 01:09:49.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said to say hi to big
brother's girlfriend, too.</b></Default>

c0001624
01:09:49.440 --> 01:09:51.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, I've had those!</b></Default>

c0001625
01:09:51.350 --> 01:09:53.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll really like 'em, big sis.</b></Default>

c0001626
01:09:53.110 --> 01:09:55.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're tasty!
- Oh, man.</b></Default>

c0001627
01:09:55.270 --> 01:09:58.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're clinging onto Mai more
than usual today, Toyohama.</b></Default>

c0001628
01:09:58.240 --> 01:10:00.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did your sister obsession
get even worse?</b></Default>

c0001629
01:10:00.820 --> 01:10:03.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She said she had a bad dream
this morning.</b></Default>

c0001630
01:10:03.410 --> 01:10:05.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One where I got into
a traffic accident.</b></Default>

c0001631
01:10:05.740 --> 01:10:06.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001632
01:10:07.370 --> 01:10:08.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

c0001633
01:10:08.660 --> 01:10:10.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can't do much about that.</b></Default>

c0001634
01:10:10.420 --> 01:10:13.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My Mai can spoil you all
you want just for today.</b></Default>

c0001635
01:10:13.460 --> 01:10:15.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, I don't need
your permission, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0001636
01:10:15.500 --> 01:10:18.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nodoka, feel free
to step on Sakuta's foot.</b></Default>

c0001637
01:10:18.210 --> 01:10:19.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, what?
[both laughing]</b></Default>

c0001638
01:10:19.870 --> 01:10:19.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 26TH
- Uh, what?
[both laughing]</b></Default>

c0001639
01:10:19.880 --> 01:10:22.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 26TH</b></Default>

c0001640
01:10:26.180 --> 01:10:27.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[freezer humming]</b></Default>

c0001641
01:10:34.110 --> 01:10:36.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I really hope that
Shoko-chan's able to get better.</b></Default>

c0001642
01:10:37.320 --> 01:10:38.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
Oh?</b></Default>

c0001643
01:10:41.820 --> 01:10:43.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001644
01:10:43.160 --> 01:10:45.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is something wrong?
- This is...</b></Default>

c0001645
01:10:48.870 --> 01:10:50.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Futaba.</b></Default>

c0001646
01:10:50.460 --> 01:10:52.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makinohara's puberty syndrome</b></Default>

c0001647
01:10:52.080 --> 01:10:54.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is still unresolved
at this point, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0001648
01:10:55.880 --> 01:10:58.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The one writing and erasing
the sentences on that print-out</b></Default>

c0001649
01:10:58.920 --> 01:11:00.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is the her that's back
in fourth grade.</b></Default>

c0001650
01:11:00.880 --> 01:11:02.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Am I right?</b></Default>

c0001651
01:11:02.930 --> 01:11:04.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makinohara from three years
in the past</b></Default>

c0001652
01:11:04.840 --> 01:11:06.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is anxious about her future.</b></Default>

c0001653
01:11:07.010 --> 01:11:08.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's the true root cause</b></Default>

c0001654
01:11:08.720 --> 01:11:10.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of her puberty syndrome,
correct?</b></Default>

c0001655
01:11:10.810 --> 01:11:14.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa, do you understand
what you're implying with that?</b></Default>

c0001656
01:11:14.730 --> 01:11:18.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The place we're in right now
is not really the present.</b></Default>

c0001657
01:11:18.400 --> 01:11:19.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the future.</b></Default>

c0001658
01:11:20.400 --> 01:11:23.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So wouldn't that mean that
if we were able to save</b></Default>

c0001659
01:11:23.400 --> 01:11:25.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the present Makinohara
that's in fourth grade</b></Default>

c0001660
01:11:25.700 --> 01:11:27.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then the Makinohara
in seventh grade</b></Default>

c0001661
01:11:27.530 --> 01:11:30.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's current to us would also
be saved?</b></Default>

c0001662
01:11:30.450 --> 01:11:32.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- This is different than keeping</b></Default>

c0001663
01:11:32.160 --> 01:11:33.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a traffic accident
from happening.</b></Default>

c0001664
01:11:33.920 --> 01:11:35.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a disease. It's not going</b></Default>

c0001665
01:11:35.500 --> 01:11:38.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to magically heal simply
by restarting.</b></Default>

c0001666
01:11:38.540 --> 01:11:41.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Toyohama mentioned on
Christmas that she had a dream</b></Default>

c0001667
01:11:41.170 --> 01:11:43.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where Mai got into
a traffic accident.</b></Default>

c0001668
01:11:44.090 --> 01:11:46.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Doesn't that mean there's
a chance memories can stay</b></Default>

c0001669
01:11:46.180 --> 01:11:48.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with people who weren't
directly involved?</b></Default>

c0001670
01:11:48.350 --> 01:11:50.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I mean, I had
a similar dream myself.</b></Default>

c0001671
01:11:50.810 --> 01:11:52.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One where I brought
a traumatized version</b></Default>

c0001672
01:11:52.680 --> 01:11:54.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of you from your house over
to mine.</b></Default>

c0001673
01:11:54.560 --> 01:11:56.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then--
- But still,</b></Default>

c0001674
01:11:56.350 --> 01:11:59.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even if pieces of current
Azusagawa's memories</b></Default>

c0001675
01:11:59.270 --> 01:12:01.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could be sent to Azusagawa
from three years ago,</b></Default>

c0001676
01:12:01.480 --> 01:12:03.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure nothing would change.</b></Default>

c0001677
01:12:03.530 --> 01:12:06.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It can't be changed. Besides--
- Besides?</b></Default>

c0001678
01:12:07.620 --> 01:12:09.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Even if you were able
to change the past,</b></Default>

c0001679
01:12:09.620 --> 01:12:12.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and Shoko-chan really was able
to overcome her illness,</b></Default>

c0001680
01:12:13.040 --> 01:12:15.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would you be okay with that,
Azusagawa?</b></Default>

c0001681
01:12:16.420 --> 01:12:18.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You need to think carefully
about the consequences.</b></Default>

c0001682
01:12:19.000 --> 01:12:20.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the fourth-grade Shoko-chan</b></Default>

c0001683
01:12:20.630 --> 01:12:22.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>doesn't develop
puberty syndrome,</b></Default>

c0001684
01:12:22.460 --> 01:12:24.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that means you'll never
have met Shoko-san</b></Default>

c0001685
01:12:24.380 --> 01:12:26.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as Shichirigahama Beach,
doesn't it?</b></Default>

c0001686
01:12:27.430 --> 01:12:28.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you never met Shoko-san,</b></Default>

c0001687
01:12:29.050 --> 01:12:30.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you would never
have considered applying</b></Default>

c0001688
01:12:30.510 --> 01:12:32.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for Minegahara High School,</b></Default>

c0001689
01:12:32.180 --> 01:12:35.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which would mean you'd also
never have met me or Kunimi.</b></Default>

c0001690
01:12:35.310 --> 01:12:38.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the same goes for Sakurajima
as well, you know.</b></Default>

c0001691
01:12:38.690 --> 01:12:40.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you telling me that
would all be okay with you?</b></Default>

c0001692
01:12:41.020 --> 01:12:43.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, of course it wouldn't.
But I--</b></Default>

c0001693
01:12:43.570 --> 01:12:45.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you honestly willing
to risk all</b></Default>

c0001694
01:12:45.490 --> 01:12:48.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of your precious memories
for a possibility so minuscule,</b></Default>

c0001695
01:12:48.450 --> 01:12:50.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it may not even exist at all?
- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0001696
01:12:55.000 --> 01:12:56.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone ringing]</b></Default>

c0001697
01:12:56.960 --> 01:12:58.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone receiver clicks]</b></Default>

c0001698
01:13:00.960 --> 01:13:03.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello. Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0001699
01:13:03.880 --> 01:13:06.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hello?
This is Makinohara calling.</b></Default>

c0001700
01:13:06.670 --> 01:13:09.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, you must be
Makinohara's mother.</b></Default>

c0001701
01:13:09.390 --> 01:13:12.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Um, can you come
and visit Shoko?</b></Default>

c0001702
01:13:12.600 --> 01:13:14.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did something happen to her?</b></Default>

c0001703
01:13:14.560 --> 01:13:19.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The doctor said Shoko probably
doesn't have much longer.</b></Default>

c0001704
01:13:19.650 --> 01:13:21.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0001705
01:13:21.360 --> 01:13:23.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0001706
01:13:29.360 --> 01:13:32.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic piano music]</b></Default>

c0001707
01:13:32.280 --> 01:13:39.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001708
01:13:41.710 --> 01:13:45.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai, you know, I really do want
to save Makinohara after all.</b></Default>

c0001709
01:13:46.170 --> 01:13:48.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, I
know.</b></Default>

c0001710
01:13:48.550 --> 01:13:50.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If that's what you want to do,
I'm okay with it.</b></Default>

c0001711
01:13:50.760 --> 01:13:52.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can go and change the past.</b></Default>

c0001712
01:13:53.180 --> 01:13:55.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't care if everything
that's happened up until now</b></Default>

c0001713
01:13:55.430 --> 01:13:56.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is erased from time.</b></Default>

c0001714
01:13:56.810 --> 01:13:58.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You mean--</b></Default>

c0001715
01:13:58.350 --> 01:13:59.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You promised me that day,
right?</b></Default>

c0001716
01:14:00.020 --> 01:14:02.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That the two of us would
find happiness together.</b></Default>

c0001717
01:14:03.270 --> 01:14:05.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's still going to happen
for us.</b></Default>

c0001718
01:14:05.480 --> 01:14:07.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We just have to take
a little detour.</b></Default>

c0001719
01:14:08.070 --> 01:14:10.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, a small one.</b></Default>

c0001720
01:14:10.150 --> 01:14:11.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's no big deal.</b></Default>

c0001721
01:14:11.700 --> 01:14:13.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're simply wiping
the slate clean</b></Default>

c0001722
01:14:13.370 --> 01:14:14.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and starting fresh.</b></Default>

c0001723
01:14:14.830 --> 01:14:17.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Exactly.
That's all there is to it.</b></Default>

c0001724
01:14:18.080 --> 01:14:20.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- When we do, I'll meet you
once again, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0001725
01:14:20.540 --> 01:14:22.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah.
- Which means I'll fall in love</b></Default>

c0001726
01:14:22.830 --> 01:14:24.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with you again.
- Yeah.</b></Default>

c0001727
01:14:25.170 --> 01:14:27.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And you'll confess your love
to me once again.</b></Default>

c0001728
01:14:31.010 --> 01:14:34.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I will. I'll make sure
to find you again.</b></Default>

c0001729
01:14:34.100 --> 01:14:36.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And when you do, we'll find
that happiness together.</b></Default>

c0001730
01:14:37.260 --> 01:14:38.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That I can promise you.</b></Default>

c0001731
01:14:48.730 --> 01:14:51.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shoko, Azusagawa just got here
to see you.</b></Default>

c0001732
01:14:52.860 --> 01:14:54.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh.</b></Default>

c0001733
01:14:55.660 --> 01:14:56.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0001734
01:15:01.710 --> 01:15:03.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Makinohara.</b></Default>

c0001735
01:15:03.580 --> 01:15:04.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hello.</b></Default>

c0001736
01:15:04.830 --> 01:15:07.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You kept your promise, huh?</b></Default>

c0001737
01:15:07.210 --> 01:15:11.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That you'd come and visit
me here every day.</b></Default>

c0001738
01:15:11.090 --> 01:15:13.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My mom filled me in earlier.</b></Default>

c0001739
01:15:13.550 --> 01:15:15.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There were some days
I couldn't come because</b></Default>

c0001740
01:15:15.340 --> 01:15:16.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of work, though.</b></Default>

c0001741
01:15:16.640 --> 01:15:18.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thank you for doing that.</b></Default>

c0001742
01:15:19.010 --> 01:15:22.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, uh, remember the schedule
of the future homework you asked</b></Default>

c0001743
01:15:22.310 --> 01:15:23.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for advice about a while back?</b></Default>

c0001744
01:15:25.100 --> 01:15:28.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, I just had this really
drawn-out dream.</b></Default>

c0001745
01:15:29.070 --> 01:15:30.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001746
01:15:30.360 --> 01:15:32.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It was so strange, too.</b></Default>

c0001747
01:15:32.450 --> 01:15:34.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was a high school student
at first</b></Default>

c0001748
01:15:34.910 --> 01:15:37.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at Shichirigahama Beach.</b></Default>

c0001749
01:15:37.450 --> 01:15:41.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was trying to cheer you up
and poking fun at you, too.</b></Default>

c0001750
01:15:42.460 --> 01:15:44.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then later on I was in college.</b></Default>

c0001751
01:15:44.710 --> 01:15:47.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I ended up staying over
at your place</b></Default>

c0001752
01:15:47.670 --> 01:15:50.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where I cooked a lot of meals
and cleaned up</b></Default>

c0001753
01:15:50.210 --> 01:15:51.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as if it were my own.</b></Default>

c0001754
01:15:51.760 --> 01:15:53.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001755
01:15:53.340 --> 01:15:56.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We went to a chapel that had
an ocean view, too.</b></Default>

c0001756
01:15:56.300 --> 01:15:58.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There I got to put on
a wedding dress.</b></Default>

c0001757
01:15:58.430 --> 01:15:59.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were red in the face</b></Default>

c0001758
01:16:00.060 --> 01:16:01.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you told me
I looked beautiful.</b></Default>

c0001759
01:16:02.640 --> 01:16:04.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if it was a dream,</b></Default>

c0001760
01:16:04.190 --> 01:16:07.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>spending my days with you
was so much fun.</b></Default>

c0001761
01:16:07.770 --> 01:16:10.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It wasn't just a dream.
Makinohara--</b></Default>

c0001762
01:16:10.520 --> 01:16:12.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It really was incredible.</b></Default>

c0001763
01:16:12.860 --> 01:16:15.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm serious. All of those
things happened in real life.</b></Default>

c0001764
01:16:18.570 --> 01:16:21.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, I
know, Sakuta.
I'm fully aware.</b></Default>

c0001765
01:16:21.410 --> 01:16:23.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?
- I understand it all.</b></Default>

c0001766
01:16:24.000 --> 01:16:27.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That what I dreamed
was my actual future life.</b></Default>

c0001767
01:16:27.290 --> 01:16:30.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And also that the current time
is the future.</b></Default>

c0001768
01:16:30.170 --> 01:16:31.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It all makes sense now.</b></Default>

c0001769
01:16:31.750 --> 01:16:33.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's right!
It's all true!</b></Default>

c0001770
01:16:33.670 --> 01:16:35.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why if we can change
the past,</b></Default>

c0001771
01:16:35.720 --> 01:16:38.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we might still be able to find
a way to save you, Makinohara.</b></Default>

c0001772
01:16:39.550 --> 01:16:41.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Even if you redo the past,</b></Default>

c0001773
01:16:41.930 --> 01:16:45.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think curing my illness
is going to be quite so simple.</b></Default>

c0001774
01:16:45.730 --> 01:16:48.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although,
the overwhelming sadness</b></Default>

c0001775
01:16:48.900 --> 01:16:50.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're carrying is different.</b></Default>

c0001776
01:16:50.820 --> 01:16:53.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do believe I can at least
rescue you from this pain.</b></Default>

c0001777
01:16:53.940 --> 01:16:55.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What are you saying?</b></Default>

c0001778
01:16:55.610 --> 01:16:57.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I can see it all.</b></Default>

c0001779
01:16:57.950 --> 01:17:01.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That I caused you agony
all along, didn't I?</b></Default>

c0001780
01:17:01.700 --> 01:17:02.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're wrong.</b></Default>

c0001781
01:17:03.080 --> 01:17:04.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>None of this
is your fault at all.</b></Default>

c0001782
01:17:05.660 --> 01:17:08.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So much happened because
of my puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

c0001783
01:17:09.330 --> 01:17:12.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the whole reason you
and I even met to begin with.</b></Default>

c0001784
01:17:12.460 --> 01:17:14.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't regret
meeting Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0001785
01:17:14.210 --> 01:17:16.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never have.
Not for an instant.</b></Default>

c0001786
01:17:17.510 --> 01:17:20.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, you sure put in
a valiant effort.</b></Default>

c0001787
01:17:20.850 --> 01:17:22.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001788
01:17:22.100 --> 01:17:24.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So you see,
it's all right now.</b></Default>

c0001789
01:17:25.060 --> 01:17:26.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll do it.</b></Default>

c0001790
01:17:26.430 --> 01:17:29.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll redo things properly
this time.</b></Default>

c0001791
01:17:29.770 --> 01:17:33.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I can create a future where
I never meet you at all.</b></Default>

c0001792
01:17:34.480 --> 01:17:35.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sniffles]</b></Default>

c0001793
01:17:36.030 --> 01:17:39.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A future where you don't have
to feel deep sorrow</b></Default>

c0001794
01:17:40.030 --> 01:17:41.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like this anymore.</b></Default>

c0001795
01:17:41.660 --> 01:17:43.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hold on!
You've got it wrong!</b></Default>

c0001796
01:17:44.030 --> 01:17:45.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not what I
was trying to say.</b></Default>

c0001797
01:17:46.620 --> 01:17:49.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm okay redoing things
for your sake, Makinohara.</b></Default>

c0001798
01:17:49.710 --> 01:17:53.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Please leave it to me.
I'll take care of everything.</b></Default>

c0001799
01:17:53.290 --> 01:17:56.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter what,
I'll make you happy, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0001800
01:17:57.050 --> 01:17:58.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So please just...</b></Default>

c0001801
01:18:01.220 --> 01:18:02.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001802
01:18:02.430 --> 01:18:03.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makinohara?</b></Default>

c0001803
01:18:04.220 --> 01:18:05.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makinohara?</b></Default>

c0001804
01:18:06.600 --> 01:18:07.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door slides open]</b></Default>

c0001805
01:18:09.270 --> 01:18:10.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How was Shoko-chan?</b></Default>

c0001806
01:18:11.310 --> 01:18:12.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She fell asleep for now.</b></Default>

c0001807
01:18:12.860 --> 01:18:14.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.</b></Default>

c0001808
01:18:16.570 --> 01:18:17.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, look.</b></Default>

c0001809
01:18:21.700 --> 01:18:22.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001810
01:18:22.620 --> 01:18:22.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SOMEDAY, I WANT TO BE A
KIND PERSON. I WILL LIVE ON,
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001811
01:18:22.660 --> 01:18:23.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SOMEDAY, I WANT TO BE A
KIND PERSON. I WILL LIVE ON,</b></Default>

c0001812
01:18:23.800 --> 01:18:24.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>CHERISHING THE PHRASES
"THANK YOU,"</b></Default>

c0001813
01:18:24.800 --> 01:18:25.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"YOU DID YOUR BEST,"</b></Default>

c0001814
01:18:25.790 --> 01:18:26.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>AND "I LOVE YOU."</b></Default>

c0001815
01:18:26.740 --> 01:18:29.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The heck is this?</b></Default>

c0001816
01:18:30.620 --> 01:18:32.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why?</b></Default>

c0001817
01:18:32.080 --> 01:18:35.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I talked
to Shoko-chan's mother.</b></Default>

c0001818
01:18:35.670 --> 01:18:38.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yesterday Shoko-chan
suddenly mentioned she wanted</b></Default>

c0001819
01:18:38.130 --> 01:18:39.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to finish her homework.</b></Default>

c0001820
01:18:40.380 --> 01:18:42.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What can I do?</b></Default>

c0001821
01:18:43.800 --> 01:18:46.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What can I do to save Makinohara
from this?</b></Default>

c0001822
01:18:48.270 --> 01:18:51.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From the very start,
she knew everything.</b></Default>

c0001823
01:18:52.350 --> 01:18:55.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All about Shoko-san,
about herself,</b></Default>

c0001824
01:18:55.650 --> 01:18:57.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and even about how she might
be able to change the past.</b></Default>

c0001825
01:19:00.280 --> 01:19:01.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0001826
01:19:02.280 --> 01:19:04.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But this is the only thing
I can come up with.</b></Default>

c0001827
01:19:06.780 --> 01:19:09.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shoko-chan really
did do her best.</b></Default>

c0001828
01:19:10.830 --> 01:19:13.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why what I think you
should do is finish her homework</b></Default>

c0001829
01:19:13.750 --> 01:19:15.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for her, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0001830
01:19:15.500 --> 01:19:17.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please let her know you saw
how hard she worked.</b></Default>

c0001831
01:19:18.750 --> 01:19:20.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0001832
01:19:20.420 --> 01:19:21.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think...</b></Default>

c0001833
01:19:21.670 --> 01:19:24.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic music]</b></Default>

c0001834
01:19:24.640 --> 01:19:31.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001835
01:19:39.150 --> 01:19:40.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0001836
01:19:42.070 --> 01:19:43.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasping]</b></Default>

c0001837
01:19:44.110 --> 01:19:45.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0001838
01:19:45.490 --> 01:19:46.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001839
01:19:47.700 --> 01:19:50.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

c0001840
01:19:50.540 --> 01:19:53.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both laughing]</b></Default>

c0001841
01:20:05.050 --> 01:20:06.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0001842
01:20:10.760 --> 01:20:13.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess it's the new year.
[grunts]</b></Default>

c0001843
01:20:18.020 --> 01:20:20.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic music]</b></Default>

c0001844
01:20:21.030 --> 01:20:27.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001845
01:21:01.940 --> 01:21:08.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001846
01:21:31.790 --> 01:21:33.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>CHALLENGE MYSELF TO CAKE-BAKING IN HIGH SCHOOL</b></Default>

c0001847
01:21:34.010 --> 01:21:36.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ma'am, I finished mine!
- Me, too!</b></Default>

c0001848
01:21:36.350 --> 01:21:37.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Same here!</b></Default>

c0001849
01:21:37.390 --> 01:21:40.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chatter and laughter]</b></Default>

c0001850
01:21:44.020 --> 01:21:45.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm all done!</b></Default>

c0001851
01:21:47.910 --> 01:21:51.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>JANUARY 6TH</b></Default>

c0001852
01:21:54.950 --> 01:21:56.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaks open]</b></Default>

c0001853
01:21:56.910 --> 01:21:58.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother.
It's morning.</b></Default>

c0001854
01:21:59.040 --> 01:22:01.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Who cares?
It's still winter break.</b></Default>

c0001855
01:22:01.420 --> 01:22:04.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're the one that said your
part-time job started today.</b></Default>

c0001856
01:22:05.000 --> 01:22:07.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you planning on practicing
going to school now, Kaede?</b></Default>

c0001857
01:22:07.760 --> 01:22:09.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I already did.</b></Default>

c0001858
01:22:09.590 --> 01:22:11.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm still super nervous
but I made it to</b></Default>

c0001859
01:22:12.010 --> 01:22:13.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the school gates today.</b></Default>

c0001860
01:22:17.850 --> 01:22:20.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Good morning.
- Good morning.</b></Default>

c0001861
01:22:20.350 --> 01:22:22.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Run away from home or something?</b></Default>

c0001862
01:22:22.150 --> 01:22:24.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I already ran away from home.</b></Default>

c0001863
01:22:24.520 --> 01:22:27.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm on my way to Saitama
to do a little mall concert.</b></Default>

c0001864
01:22:27.110 --> 01:22:28.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0001865
01:22:28.650 --> 01:22:31.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, you don't usually work
the morning shift.</b></Default>

c0001866
01:22:31.360 --> 01:22:33.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You, too.
What happened to practice?</b></Default>

c0001867
01:22:33.450 --> 01:22:34.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's in the afternoon.</b></Default>

c0001868
01:22:35.030 --> 01:22:36.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Koga, coming late like
an exec.</b></Default>

c0001869
01:22:37.080 --> 01:22:38.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
My shift just started!</b></Default>

c0001870
01:22:38.700 --> 01:22:40.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm.
- W--what?</b></Default>

c0001871
01:22:40.710 --> 01:22:43.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, it's just
that you look round.</b></Default>

c0001872
01:22:44.040 --> 01:22:47.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that mochi-smooth skin from
the holiday mochi you ate?</b></Default>

c0001873
01:22:47.130 --> 01:22:48.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You really are the worst,
Sakuta!</b></Default>

c0001874
01:22:48.840 --> 01:22:50.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heck off!</b></Default>

c0001875
01:22:50.130 --> 01:22:51.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell chimes]
- Mm?</b></Default>

c0001876
01:22:51.430 --> 01:22:53.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello, welcome in.
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001877
01:22:55.890 --> 01:22:57.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm gonna go
with the hearty carbonara.</b></Default>

c0001878
01:22:58.060 --> 01:22:59.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>S--sorry.</b></Default>

c0001879
01:22:59.430 --> 01:23:01.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll do this instead, actually.</b></Default>

c0001880
01:23:01.600 --> 01:23:03.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You don't need
to go on some restrictive diet.</b></Default>

c0001881
01:23:03.730 --> 01:23:05.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think you became round
or anything.</b></Default>

c0001882
01:23:05.860 --> 01:23:08.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, I get it.</b></Default>

c0001883
01:23:08.730 --> 01:23:11.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll be sure to inform
Sakurajima that you were looking</b></Default>

c0001884
01:23:11.200 --> 01:23:12.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at me with lewd
eyes immediately.</b></Default>

c0001885
01:23:12.860 --> 01:23:14.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'd appreciate it
if you don't</b></Default>

c0001886
01:23:14.740 --> 01:23:16.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'cause we have a New Year's
shrine date later</b></Default>

c0001887
01:23:16.620 --> 01:23:17.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she'll scold me.</b></Default>

c0001888
01:23:17.910 --> 01:23:20.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That means it's better
if I tell her, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0001889
01:23:20.450 --> 01:23:22.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well--
- Oh, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0001890
01:23:22.710 --> 01:23:24.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really are a rascal.</b></Default>

c0001891
01:23:33.760 --> 01:23:35.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- What is it?</b></Default>

c0001892
01:23:35.430 --> 01:23:37.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Do you think you could lend me
some change?</b></Default>

c0001893
01:23:37.760 --> 01:23:40.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I gave mine as a donation
at Fujisawa Station.</b></Default>

c0001894
01:23:40.600 --> 01:23:42.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Okay, then just use a bill.</b></Default>

c0001895
01:23:42.270 --> 01:23:44.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [shouting]</b></Default>

c0001896
01:23:45.060 --> 01:23:46.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah--</b></Default>

c0001897
01:23:47.270 --> 01:23:48.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[moans]</b></Default>

c0001898
01:23:49.230 --> 01:23:51.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did you make enough wishes
for your 1,000 yen?</b></Default>

c0001899
01:23:51.820 --> 01:23:54.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I at least made an adamant
wish that I wouldn't encounter</b></Default>

c0001900
01:23:54.320 --> 01:23:56.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so many strange and stressful
incidents in the new year.</b></Default>

c0001901
01:23:56.950 --> 01:23:59.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There certainly were a lot.</b></Default>

c0001902
01:23:59.410 --> 01:24:02.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's thanks to one of those
that you were able to meet me.</b></Default>

c0001903
01:24:02.540 --> 01:24:04.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think at this point
I've had my fill</b></Default>

c0001904
01:24:04.370 --> 01:24:05.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of wild bunny girls, though.</b></Default>

c0001905
01:24:05.960 --> 01:24:07.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both laughing]</b></Default>

c0001906
01:24:11.510 --> 01:24:13.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You really love the ocean,
don't you, Sakuta?</b></Default>

c0001907
01:24:13.670 --> 01:24:16.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not nearly as much
as I love you, though, Mai.</b></Default>

c0001908
01:24:16.340 --> 01:24:18.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I guess you really love
that high school girl</b></Default>

c0001909
01:24:18.470 --> 01:24:19.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you saw in your dreams.</b></Default>

c0001910
01:24:19.890 --> 01:24:21.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is the spot
where you two went</b></Default>

c0001911
01:24:21.560 --> 01:24:22.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on all those dates, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0001912
01:24:23.020 --> 01:24:25.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I mean, yeah, but they
all happened in my dreams.</b></Default>

c0001913
01:24:25.690 --> 01:24:28.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Mai, you're quite fond
of this place, too, aren't you?</b></Default>

c0001914
01:24:28.860 --> 01:24:31.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In my case I'm only attached
to this place because</b></Default>

c0001915
01:24:31.440 --> 01:24:33.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I spent some time filming
a movie out here.</b></Default>

c0001916
01:24:35.650 --> 01:24:38.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A girl with heart disease
awaiting a donor.</b></Default>

c0001917
01:24:38.820 --> 01:24:40.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I first received the offer,</b></Default>

c0001918
01:24:40.410 --> 01:24:42.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got this feeling I had
to play this role.</b></Default>

c0001919
01:24:42.660 --> 01:24:45.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I totally bawled watching it.</b></Default>

c0001920
01:24:45.460 --> 01:24:47.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And everyone else in
the theater cried, too.</b></Default>

c0001921
01:24:47.920 --> 01:24:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Even to this day,
I don't get it.</b></Default>

c0001922
01:24:50.170 --> 01:24:53.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why I felt that I had
to play that role so strongly.</b></Default>

c0001923
01:24:53.210 --> 01:24:54.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to do something,
though.</b></Default>

c0001924
01:24:55.630 --> 01:24:57.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's like how you donate money.</b></Default>

c0001925
01:25:00.220 --> 01:25:02.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Running is dangerous!
Careful!</b></Default>

c0001926
01:25:03.350 --> 01:25:06.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Please just watch your step!
- It's okay! I'm fine!</b></Default>

c0001927
01:25:06.520 --> 01:25:08.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Dad, Mom!
Come on, let's go!</b></Default>

c0001928
01:25:08.980 --> 01:25:10.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Over here!</b></Default>

c0001929
01:25:10.480 --> 01:25:11.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001930
01:25:12.020 --> 01:25:13.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta?</b></Default>

c0001931
01:25:14.070 --> 01:25:15.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That girl.</b></Default>

c0001932
01:25:15.900 --> 01:25:17.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [laughing]
Hey, hurry up!</b></Default>

c0001933
01:25:19.240 --> 01:25:20.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Someone you know?</b></Default>

c0001934
01:25:22.280 --> 01:25:23.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's not.</b></Default>

c0001935
01:25:25.700 --> 01:25:26.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0001936
01:25:27.040 --> 01:25:28.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic music]</b></Default>

c0001937
01:25:28.960 --> 01:25:30.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shudders]</b></Default>

c0001938
01:25:30.540 --> 01:25:37.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001939
01:25:37.550 --> 01:25:38.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makinohara!</b></Default>

c0001940
01:25:43.470 --> 01:25:44.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0001941
01:25:45.600 --> 01:25:46.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

c0001942
01:25:47.730 --> 01:25:50.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0001943
01:25:50.400 --> 01:25:52.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, Sakuta!</b></Default>

c0001944
01:25:53.480 --> 01:25:55.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

c0001945
01:25:56.990 --> 01:25:59.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0001946
01:26:00.030 --> 01:26:02.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>["Fukashigi no Carte" plays]</b></Default>

c0001947
01:26:02.950 --> 01:26:09.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001948
01:26:34.820 --> 01:26:41.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001949
01:27:04.300 --> 01:27:11.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001950
01:27:32.160 --> 01:27:39.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001951
01:28:04.820 --> 01:28:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001952
01:28:45.360 --> 01:28:52.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0001953
01:29:15.100 --> 01:29:25.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

